K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:17b-25: tsha ba'i sems can dmyal ba gang yin pa de dag tu ni bsil bar gyur te 'bab bo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:17b-27: de nas sems can de dag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:17b-28: de nas de dag 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:17b-32: 'on te gzhan du skyes sam snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:17b-33: de nas de dag dad pa bskyed pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das sprul pa 'gyed par mdzad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18a-0: de dag gis sprul pa mthong nas @18a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18a-3: bdag cag ni 'di nas kyang shi 'phos bar ma gyur la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18a-4: gzhan du'ang ma skyes mod kyi 'on kyang sngon ma byung ba'i sems can snang ba 'di'i mthus bdag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18a-5: de nas de dag sprul pa de la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18a-9: steng du 'gro ba gang yin pa de dag ni rgyal chen bzhi'i ris rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18a-10: sum cu rtsa gsum pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18a-16: tshangs pa'i mdun na 'don pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18a-17: tshangs pa chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18a-25: bsod nams skyes rnams dang; 'bras bu che rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-0: 'og min gyi lha rnams kyi bar du song @18b nas mi rtag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-3: bdag med pa'i sgra sgrogs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-4: tshigs su bcad pa gnyis kyang rjod par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-5: nges par 'byung ba brtsam par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-6: sangs rgyas bstan la sbyor bar gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-7: 'dam bu'i khyim la glang chen bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-8: 'chi bdag sde ni gzhom par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-10: bag yod spyod par byed pa ni; ;skye ba'i 'khor ba rab spangs nas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-11: sdug bsngal zad par byed par 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-13: de nas 'od zer de dag gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams bskor nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-14: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi phyi bzhin 'brang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-15: gal te bcom ldan 'das kyis 'das pa'i las lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-16: bcom ldan 'das kyi snam logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-17: ma 'ongs pa'i las lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-18: mdun logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-19: sems can dmyal bar skye bar lung ston par bzheng na ni; zhabs kyi mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-20: dud 'gror skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-21: zhabs kyi rting par mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-22: yi dvags su skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-23: zhabs kyi mthe bor mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-24: mir skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:18b-25: pus mo gnyis su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-1: rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-2: phyag g-yon pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-3: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-4: phyag g-yas pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-5: lhar skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-6: lte bar mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-7: nyan thos kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni; zhal du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-8: rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-9: smin mtshams kyi mdzod spur mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-10: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-11: dbu'i gtsug tor du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-12: de nas 'od zer de dag gis bcom ldan 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-13: bcom ldan 'das kyi dbu'i gtsug tor du mi snang bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-14: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-15: thal mo sbyar te bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-16: tshon sna stong gis spel ba sna tshogs can //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-17: mang po zhal gyi sgo nas byung bar gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-18: de yis phyogs rnams kun tu snang bar bgyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-19: nyi ma shar bas ji ltar bgyis pa bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-20: yang tshigs su bcad de gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-21: rgod dang bral zhing rgyags dang mi dgyes spangs pa yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19a-22: sangs rgyas 'gro ba dag gi dam pa'i rgyur gyur pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-0: rgyal ba dgra thub rnams @19b ni rgyu rkyen ma mchis par //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-1: padma'i rtsa dang dung mdog lta bu'i 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-2: brtan pos nyid kyi blo yis dus bab mkhyen lags na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-3: dge sbyong rgyal dbang nyan pa som nyi 'tshal ba rnams //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-4: thub pa khyu mchog gi ni gsung mchog bstan pa dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-5: bzang po dag gis the tshom skyes pa bsal bar gsol //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-6: rgya mtsho dang ni ri rgyal lta bur brtan pa yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-7: mgon po rdzogs sangs rgyas rnams gyin 'da' 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-8: gang gi don du dpa' bo 'dzum pa ston mdzad pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-9: de ni khyod las skye bo phal cher nyan par 'tshal //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-10: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-15: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams ni rgyu med rkyen med par 'dzum pa mi mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-17: khye'u le lo can 'dis nga la 'di lta bu'i bkur sti byas pa mthong ngam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-21: khye'u le lo can 'dis dge ba'i rtsa ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-23: sbyin par bya ba'i chos yongs su gtong pa 'dis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-24: bskal pa grangs med pa gsum gyis yang dag par bsgrub par bya ba'i byang chub yang dag par bsgrubs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:19b-25: snying rje chen pos yongs su bsgos pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs par byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-0: ma 'dres pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gsum @20a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-1: dang; snying rje chen po dang ldan pa'i yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas stobs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-3: mthu rtsal dang shin tu ldan pa zhes bya bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-5: de'i sbyin par bya ba'i chos ni gang nga la mngon par dga' bar gyur pa 'di yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas dge slong de dag yi rangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-8: gang po la sogs pa'i rtogs pa brjod pa brgya pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-9: bam po gnyis pa; ded dpon zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-10: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-11: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-13: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-21: mi'am ci rnams dang; lto 'phye chen po rnams kyi bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-29: nam mkha' lding dang mi'am ci dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20a-30: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-4: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-5: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' rab na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-6: de'i tshe mnyan du yod pa na ded dpon chen po zhig rgya mtsho chen po'i nang du gru bub ste phyir 'ongs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-7: des lan gnyis lan gsum gyi bar du lha thams cad la gsol ba btab ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-8: rgya mtsho chen po'i nang du zhugs na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-9: 'on kyang gru bub ste phyir 'ongs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-10: de nas de mi dga' ba chen po skyes nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-12: bdag gis thabs gang gis nor bsdu bar bya ba'i thabs ci yod snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-13: yang de 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-14: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'di ni lha thams cad las kyang ches khyad par du 'phags pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-16: gzhan la phan pa la zhugs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-20: skye dgu la mnyes gshin pa yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-21: da ni bdag gis 'di la brten te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-22: yang rgya mtsho chen po'i nang du zhugs la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-23: gru'i don legs par grub ste phyir 'ongs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-24: nor phyed kyis 'di la mchod pa bya'o snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-25: des de ltar brtson 'grus byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-26: yang rgya mtsho chen po'i nang du zhugs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-27: sangs rgyas kyi mthus rin po che'i gling du phyin nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:20b-28: rin po che chen po bsdus te bde ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-1: med par bdag gi khyim du phyin to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-2: de ngal bso nas snod bzlugs na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-3: des rin po che rnam pa sna tshogs mthong nas chags pa chen po skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-4: bdag gis rin po che 'di lta bu dag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-5: dge sbyong goo ta ma la phyed ji ltar sbyin snyam du sems pa la zhugs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-7: bdag gis 'di rnams bdag gi chung ma'i lag tu zho'i bzhi cha gcig tu btsongs la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-8: bcom ldan 'das la spos dbul bar bya gor ma chag snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-9: des zho'i bzhi cha gcig gis aa ka ru'i spos nyos nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-10: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal du song ngo; ;de nas shin tu ngo tsha bzhin du sgo khang du 'dug nas aa ka rus bdugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-11: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gang gis bdug pa de steng gi nam mkha' la yang dag par 'phags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-12: mnyan du yod pa thams cad khyab par gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-13: sprin chen po'i mgo ltar 'dug par 'gyur ba de lta bu'i rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du bya ba mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-14: des lha dang; mi dad par byed pa'i cho 'phrul shin tu rmad du byung ba de mthong nas dga' ba chen po skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-15: bdag gi sems la brgyad bkag nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21a-16: gang bdag gis rin po che'i sgo nas bcom ldan 'das kyi sku bslub 'di ni bdag gi cha ma yin no zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-0: de nas dad dpon des bcom ldan 'das nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa khyim gyi @21b nang du bshos la spyan drangs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-1: de nas zhal zas bzang pos tshim par byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-2: rin po che chen po dag gis gtor to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-3: de nas rin po che de dag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-5: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sangs rgyas kyi mthu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-6: lha rnams kyi lha'i mthus bcom ldan 'das kyi dbu'i steng gi nam mkha' la 'phags nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-7: rin po che'i khang pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-8: khang pa brtsegs pa rin po che'i rgyal mtshan can /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-10: mgar ba'i slob ma legs par lobs pas kyang byed mi nus pa de lta bur gyur te 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-11: de nas ded dpon des cho 'phrul de mthong nas ched kyis dga' ba skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-12: sdong po rtsa ba nas bcad pa bzhin du bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag btsal nas smon lam btab pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-15: sbyin par bya ba'i chos yongs su gtong ba 'dis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-16: bdag 'jig rten long ba 'dren pa med cing yongs su 'dren pa med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-17: sems can ma brgal ba rnams sgrol ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-18: ma grol ba rnams 'grol ba dang; dbugs ma phyin pa rnams dbugs 'byin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-19: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan las zlo ba'i sangs rgyas su gyur cig ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-20: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis ded dpon de'i rgyu gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:21b-21: las gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa mkhyen nas 'dzum pa mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-1: 'das rnams gang gi tshe 'dzum pa mdzad pa'i chos nyid de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-2: de'i tshe zhal gyi sgo nas 'od zer sngon po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-5: dkar po rnams byung nas; kha cig ni 'og tu 'gro'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-7: 'og tu 'gro ba gang yin pa de dag ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-8: sems can dmyal ba yang sos dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-21: autpa la ltar gas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-23: padma ltar gas pa chen por song nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-24: tsha ba'i sems can dmyal ba gang yin pa de dag tu ni bsil bar gyur te 'bab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-25: grang ba'i sems can dmyal ba gang yin pa de dag tu ni dro bar gyur te 'bab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-26: des na sems can de dag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-27: de nas de dag 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-31: 'on te gzhan du skyes sam snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-32: de nas de dag dad pa bskyed pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das sprul pa 'gyed par mdzad do /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-33: de dag gis sprul pa mthong nas 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-35: bdag cag ni 'di nas kyang shi 'phos par ma gyur la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22a-36: gzhan du'ang ma skyes mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-0: 'on kyang sngon ma @22b byung ba'i sems can snang ba 'di'i mthus bdag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-1: de nas de dag sprul pa la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-2: sems can dmyal ba myong bar 'gyur ba'i las de zad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-4: mi rnams kyi nang du gang du bden pa rnams kyi snod du rung bar 'gyur ba der nying mtshams 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-5: steng du 'gro ba gang yin pa de dag ni rgyal chen bzhi'i ris rnams dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-8: dga' ldan rnams dang; 'phrul dga' rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-11: tshangs pa'i mdun na 'don pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-12: tshangs pa chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-26: 'og min gyi bar gyi lha rnams kyi nang du song nas mi rtag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-27: sdug bsngal ba dang; stong pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-28: bdag med pa'i sgra sgrogs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:22b-29: tshigs su bcad pa gnyis kyang rjod par byed de /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24a-0: thub pa khyu mchog gi ni gsung mchog @24a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24a-2: bzang po dag gis the tshom skyes pa bsal bar gsol //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24a-23: snying rje chen po dang ldan pa'i yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas spos mchog ces bya bar 'gyur te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24b-1: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24b-2: zla ba zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24b-3: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24b-4: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24b-5: phyug po rnams dang; pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24b-14: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:24b-29: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-0: de nas mnyan du yod pa na tha ga pa zla ba zhes bya ba dbul zhing mchog tu dbul ba zhig @25a *//

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-3: des cung zad kyang gzhag tu med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-4: de nas de 'di snyam du sems te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-6: 'dir yang dge ba mi byed pas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-7: 'di nas 'jig rten pha rol tu'ang bsod nams kyang ma byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-9: 'jigs shing skrag pa'i mgon skyabs kyang ma byas par 'gro dgos srid kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-10: bdag gis bcom ldan 'das la sna 'ga' zhig gis mchod par bya gor ma chag snyam mo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-12: ras de las ras kyi tshar tshar khyer te srang du zhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-13: bcom ldan 'das snga dro sham thabs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-16: mnyan du yod par bsod snyoms la gshegs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:25a-17: de nas des sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das sku mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis legs par brgyan pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:27b-20: dge sbyong rgyal dbang nyan pa som nyi 'tshal ba rnams //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:27b-21: thub pa khyu mchog gi ni gsung mchog brtan pa dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:27b-22: bzang po dag gis the tshom skyes pa bsal bar gsol //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-0: rgya mtsho dang ni ri rgyal @28a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-2: mgon po rdzogs sangs rgyas rnams gyin 'da' 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-3: gang gi don du dpa' bo 'dzum pa ston mdzad pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-4: de ni khyod las skye bo phal cher nyan par 'tshal //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-5: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-10: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams ni rgyu med rkyen med par 'dzum pa mi mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-12: tha ga pa zla ba 'dis nga la 'di lta bu'i bkur sti byas pa mthong ngam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-16: tha ga pa zla ba 'di'i dge ba'i rtsa ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-18: sbyin par bya ba'i chos yongs su gtong ba 'dis bskal pa grangs med pa gsum gyis yang dag par bsgrub par bya ba'i byang chub yang dag par bsgrubs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-19: snying rje chen pos yongs su bsgos pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs par byas nas stobs bcu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-21: ma 'dres pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gsum dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28a-22: snying rje chen po dang ldan pa'i yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas tshar tshar bla ma zhes bya bar 'gyur te 'jig rten du 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-0: de'i sbyin par bya ba'i chos ni gang nga la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur pa 'di @28b yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-1: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-2: dge slong de dag yi rangs ste bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-3: che ba zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-4: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-5: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-7: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-16: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-25: mi'am ci dang; lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-31: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-32: de'i tshe mnyan du yod pa na tshong dpon gyi bu che ba zhes bya ba zhig gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:28b-33: de yang khro ba'i kun nas dkris pa shas che ba zhig ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-1: sogs pa ston pa drug la mchod pa byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-2: de phyis nad tshabs chen po zhig gis thebs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-6: shi la thug nas 'di snyam du bsams te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-7: da ni bdag sdug bsngal bar 'gyur ba'i skyabs byed pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-8: srog phangs pa sbyin par byed pa sangs rgyas ma yin pa gzhan su zhig yod snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-9: de nas de ltar bsams nas bcom ldan 'das la gsol ba 'debs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-10: de'i skabs su sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis ni mi mkhyen pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-13: thugs su mi chud pa ci yang med la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-14: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-15: 'jig rten la phan 'dogs pa la zhugs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-16: srung ba gcig pa dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-22: rig pa gsum snang bar mdzad pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-23: bslab pa gsum la legs par bslabs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-24: 'dul ba'i gzhi gsum la mkhas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-25: chu bo bzhi las brgal ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-26: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi'i zhabs kyi mthil shin tu brtan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-27: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi la yun ring nas 'dris par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29a-29: khyu mchog gi yang dag pa'i seng ge'i sgra chen po sgrogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-0: yan lag lnga rnam par @29b spangs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-1: 'gro ba lnga las yang dag par 'das pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-2: yan lag drug dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-3: pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-4: rtag tu gnas par bya ba drug la gnas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-5: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun gyi me tog gis phyug pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-6: lam yan lag brgyad pa ston pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-7: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu la mkhas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-8: stobs bcu'i stobs dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-9: phyogs bcur grags pas kun tu rgyas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-10: brgya phrag bcu la dbang byed pa bas kyang ches khyad par du 'phags pa rnams ni chos nyid kyis nyin dus gsum /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-11: mtshan dus gsum du sangs rgyas kyi spyan gyis 'jig rten la gzigs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-14: su ni nyam nga bar gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-15: su ni gnod pa dang ldan /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-19: su ni ngan song du gzhol /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-21: su ni ngan song du bab /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-22: su ni ngas ngan song nas phyung ste mtho ris dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-25: su ni 'dod pa'i 'dam du bying ba las lag nas drang bar bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-26: su ni 'phags pa'i nor bdun med pa las 'phags pa'i nor bdun gyi dbang phyug la dbang byed du gzhug par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-27: su ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams ma bskyed pa las bskyed par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:29b-28: su ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams bskyed zin pa las yongs su smin par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-0: su ni yongs su smin zin pa las rnam @30a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-1: par grol bar bya snyam du ye shes gzigs pa 'jug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-3: rgya mtsho chu srin rnams kyi gnas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-4: dus rlabs yol bar 'gyur yang srid //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-5: gdul bar bya ba'i sras rnams la //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-6: sangs rgyas dus las yol ba med //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-7: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshong dpon gyi bu che ba'i gnas skabs de gzigs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-8: 'od zer gser gyi kha dog can /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-9: nyi ma stong gi 'od las lhag pa dag bkye ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-10: de dag gis khyim de kun tu snang bar byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-11: bskal pa stong du yongs su bsgoms pa'i byams pa'i 'od zer dag kyang bkye ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-12: de dag gis de'i lus la phog ma thag tu rab tu sim par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-13: de nas bcom ldan 'das de'i sgo khang du gshegs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-14: sgo srung gi mis bcom ldan 'das sgo nas bzhugs so zhes de la sbran to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-15: de nas tshong dpon gyi bu che ba dga' bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-16: dbugs ma phyin pa dbugs phyin par gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-21: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal mthong bar 'tshal lo zhes gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-22: de nas bcom ldan 'das nang du gshegs nas gdan bshams pa la bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-23: bzhugs nas kyang bcom ldan 'das kyis che ba la bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30a-24: che ba khyod la gnod pa ci zhig yod /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-1: bdag la lus kyi gnod pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-2: sems kyi gnod pa mchis so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-3: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis de la sems can thams cad la byams pa'i sems kyis gdams ngag bstan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-4: 'di ni khyod kyi sems kyi sdug bsngal gyi gnyen po yin no zhes bka' stsal to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-5: de nas 'jig rten pa'i thugs bskyed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-7: lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis ri spos kyi ngad ldang las sman shi ri ka khyer te 'ongs na legs so snyam du dgongs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis thugs bskyed pa'i mod la lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis ri spos kyi ngad ldang las sman shi ri ka blangs te bcom ldan 'das la phul lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-9: bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang nyid kyi phyag tu bzhes nas che ba la byin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-10: 'di ni khyod kyi lus kyi sdug bsngal tsha ba zhi bar byed pa yin no zhes bka' stsal to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-12: sems shin tu sbyangs pa'i bde ba thob nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-13: bcom ldan 'das la sems dga' bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-14: sems dga' bar gyur nas rgyal po gsal rgyal la bsnyad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-15: bcom ldan 'das nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa bshos gsol nas 'bum ri ba'i na bza' phul te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-17: spos dang; me tog phreng thams cad kyis kyang mchod pa byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:30b-18: de nas sems la rtas par byas te smon lam btab pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-1: ba'i chos yongs su btang ba 'dis ji ltar bcom ldan 'das bla na med pa'i sman pa'i rgyal pos bdag gsos pa bzhin du bdag kyang ma 'ongs pa'i dus na 'jig rten long ba 'dren pa med cing 'dren pa med par sems can ma brgal ba rnams sgrol ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-2: ma grol ba rnams 'grol ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-3: dbugs ma phyin pa rnams 'byin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-4: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan las zlo ba'i sangs rgyas su gyur cig ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-5: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis che ba'i rgyu gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-6: las gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa mkhyen nas 'dzum pa mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-7: 'di ni sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams gang gi tshe 'dzum pa mdzad pa'i chos nyid de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-8: de'i tshe zhal nas 'od zer sngon po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-14: 'og tu 'gro ba gang yin pa de dag ni sems can dmyal ba yang sos dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-21: mnar med pa dang; chu bur can dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31a-26: autpa la ltar gas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-0: padma ltar @31b gas pa chen por song nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-1: tsha ba'i sems can dmyal ba gnag yin pa de dag tu ni bsil bar gyur te 'bab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-2: grang ba'i sems can dmyal ba gang yin pa de dag tu ni dro bar gyur te 'bab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-3: de nas sems can de dag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-4: de nas de dag 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-7: 'on te gzhan du skyes sam snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-8: de nas de dag dad pa bskyed pa'i phyir /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-9: bcom ldan 'das sprul pa 'gyed par mdzad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-10: de dag gis sprul pa mthong nas 'di snyam du sems te; kye; bdag cag ni 'di nas kyang shi 'phos par ma gyur la gzhan du'ang ma skyes mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-11: 'on kyang sngon ma byung ba'i sems can snang ba 'di'i mthus bdag cag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-12: de nas de dag sprul pa la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-13: sems can dmyal ba myong bar 'gyur ba'i las de zad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-14: lha dang; mi rnams kyi nang du gang du bden pa rnams kyi snod du rung bar 'gyur ba de nying mtshams 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-15: steng du 'gro ba gang yin pa de dag ni rgyal chen bzhi'i ris rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:31b-16: sum cu rtsa gsum pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-2: tshangs pa'i mdun na 'don pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-3: tshangs pa chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-17: 'og min gyi lha rnams kyi bar du song nas mi rtag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-20: bdag med pa'i sgra sgrogs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-21: tshigs su bcad pa gnyis kyang rjod par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-22: nges par 'byung ba brtsam par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-23: sangs rgyas bstan la sbyor bar gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-24: 'dam bu'i khyim la glang chen bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-25: 'chi bdag sde ni gzhom par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-27: bag yod spyod par byed pa ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-28: skye ba'i 'khor ba rab spangs nas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-29: sdug bsngal zad par byed par 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-31: de nas 'od zer de dag gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams bskor nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-32: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi phyi bzhin 'brang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-33: gal te bcom ldan 'das kyis 'das pa'i las lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32a-34: bcom ldan 'das kyi snam logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-0: ma 'ongs pa'i @32b las lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-1: mdun logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-2: sems can dmyal bar skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-3: zhabs ki mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-4: dud 'gror skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-5: zhabs kyi rting bar mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-6: yi dvags su skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-7: zhabs kyi mthe bor mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-8: mir skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-9: pus mo gnyis su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-10: stobs kyi 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-11: phyag g-yon pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-12: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-13: phyag g-yas pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-14: lhar skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-15: lte bar mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-16: nyan thos kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-17: zhal du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-18: rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-19: smin mtshams kyi mdzod spur mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-20: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-21: dbu'i gtsug tor du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-22: de nas 'od zer de dag gis bcom ldan 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-23: bcom ldan 'das kyi dbu'i gtsug tor du mi snang bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:32b-24: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos thal mo sbyar te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:33a-1: pa; tshon sna stong gis spel ba sna tshogs can //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:33a-2: mang po zhal gyi sgo nas byung bar gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:33a-3: de yis phyogs rnams kun tu snang bar bgyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:33a-4: nyi ma shar bas ji ltar bgyis pa bzhin //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:38b-1: de'i tshe byang phyogs kyi panytsa la'i rgyal po lho phyogs kyi panytsa la'i rgyal po dang mi mthun par gyur to //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:38b-4: phyogs gcig tu 'dug nas bcom ldan 'das la ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis 'di skad ces gsol to //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:38b-10: de gnyis phan tshun du skye bo mang po kha 'dog par bgyid na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:38b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis thugs brtse ba'i slad du de gnyis yun ring po nas 'khon byung ba zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:38b-12: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal la cang mi gsung bas gnang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:38b-13: de nas ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:38b-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis cang mi gsung bas gnang bar rig ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:38b-15: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la mgo bos phyag btsal nas stan las langs te song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:38b-16: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis de'i phyi de nyin gyi snga dro sham thabs dang chos gos gsol te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-2: mthar gyis rgyu zhing gshegs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-3: w'a ra n'a sir byon nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-4: w'a ra n'a si na drang srong smra ba'i ri dvags kyi nags na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-5: de nas re zhig na de gnyis kyis bcom ldan 'das bdag cag gi yul du gshegs par rig go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-6: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs kyis dpung gi tshogs yan lag bzhi pa sprul nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-7: byang phyogs kyi panytsa la'i rgyal po skrag cing bred nas des shing rta gcig zhon te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-8: bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du song nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-9: bcom ldan 'das kyis de la 'khon 'byang bar 'gyur ba'i chos bstan to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-10: des chos de thos nas bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du rab tu byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-11: des brtson pa dang; sgrub pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-12: 'bad pas nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-13: dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-14: lho phyogs kyi panytsa la'i rgyal pos kyang bcom ldan 'das nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa zla ba gsum gyi bar du spyan drangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-15: zhal zas ro brgya dang ldan pa gsol nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-16: 'bum ri ba'i na bza' yang phul te smon lam btab pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39a-19: sbyin par bya ba'i chos yongs su gtong ba 'dis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39b-0: bdag 'jig rten long ba 'dren pa med cing yongs su 'dren pa med @39b par sems can ma brgal ba rnams sgrol ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39b-1: ma grol ba rnams 'grol ba dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39b-6: 'di ni sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams gang gi tshe 'dzum pa mdzad pa'i chos nyid de /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39b-27: padma ltar gas pa chen por song nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39b-28: tsha ba'i sems can dmyal ba gang yin pa de dag tu ni bsil bar gyur te 'bab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:39b-29: grang ba'i sems can dmyal ba gang yin pa de dag tu ni dro bar gyur te 'bab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-0: des na sems can de dag gi @40a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-1: gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-2: de nas de dag 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-6: 'on te gzhan du skyes sam snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-7: de nas de dag dad pa bskyed pa'i phyir /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-8: bcom ldan 'das sprul pa 'gyed par mdzad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-9: de dag gis sprul pa de mthong nas 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-11: bdag cag ni 'di nas kyang shi 'phos par ma gyur la gzhan du yang ma skyes mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-12: 'on kyang sngon ma byung ba'i sems can snang ba 'di'i mthus bdag cag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-13: de nas de dag sprul pa la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-14: sems can dmyal ba myong bar 'gyur ba'i las de zad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-16: mi rnams kyi nang du gang du bden pa rnams kyi snod du rung bar 'gyur ba der nying mtshams 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-17: steng du 'gro ba gang yin pa de dag ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-18: rgyal chen bzhi'i ris rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-19: sum cu rtsa gsum pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-24: tshangs ris rnams dang; tshangs pa'i mdun na 'don pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40a-25: tshangs pa chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-10: 'og min gyi lha rnams kyi bar du song nas mi rtag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-13: bdag med pa'i sgra sgrogs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-14: tshigs su bcad pa gnyis kyang rjod par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-15: nges par 'byung ba brtsam par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-16: sangs rgyas bstan la sbyor bar gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-17: 'dam bu'i khyim la glang chen bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-18: 'chi bdag sde ni gzhom par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-20: bag yod spyod par byed pa ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-21: skye ba'i 'khor ba rab spangs nas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-22: sdug bsngal zad par byed par 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-24: de nas 'od zer de dag gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams bskor nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-25: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi phyi bzhin 'brang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-26: gal te bcom ldan 'das kyis 'das pa'i las lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-27: bcom ldan 'das kyi snam logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-28: ma 'ongs pa'i las lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-29: mdun logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-30: sems can dmyal bar skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-31: zhabs kyi mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:40b-32: dud 'gror skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-0: zhabs kyi rting par mi snang bar 'gyur @41a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-1: ro; ;yi dvags su skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-2: zhabs kyi mthe bor mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-3: mir skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-4: pus mo gnyis su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-5: stobs kyi 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-6: phyag g-yon pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-7: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-8: phyag g-yas pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-9: lhar skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-10: lte bar mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-11: nyan thos kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-12: zhal du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-13: rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-14: smin mtshams kyi mdzod spur mi snang bar 'gyur ro; ;bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-15: dbu'i gtsug tor du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-16: de nas 'od zer de dag gis bcom ldan 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-17: bcom ldan 'das kyi dbu'i gtsug tor du mi snang bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-18: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos thal mo sbyar te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-20: tshon sna stong gis spel ba sna tshogs can //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-21: mang po zhal gyi sgo nas byung bar gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41a-22: de yis phyogs rnams kun tu snang bar bgyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-0: nyi ma shar bas ji ltar bgyis @41b pa bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-1: yang tshigs su bcad de gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-2: rgod dang bral zhing rgyags dang mi dgyes spang pa yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-3: sangs rgyas 'gro ba dag gi dam pa'i rgyur gyur pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-4: rgyal ba dgra thub rnams ni rgyu rkyen ma mchis par //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-5: padma'i rtsa dang dung mdog lta bu'i 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-6: brtan pos nyid kyi blo yis dus bab mkhyen lags na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-7: dge sbyong rgyal dbang nyan pa som nyi 'tshal ba rnams //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-8: thub pa khyu mchog gi ni gsung mchog brtan pa dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-9: bzang po dag gis the tshom skyes pa bsal bar gsol //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-10: rgya mtsho dang ni ri rgyal lta bur brtan pa yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-11: mgon po rdzogs sangs rgyas rnams gyin 'da' 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-12: gang gi don du dpa' bo 'dzum pa ston mdzad pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-13: de ni khyod las skye bo phal chen nyan par 'tshal //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-19: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams ni rgyu med rkyen med par 'dzum pa mi mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-22: nga la 'di lta bu'i bkur sti byas pa mthong ngam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-26: panytsa la'i rgyal po 'di dge ba'i rtsa ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:41b-28: sbyin par bya ba'i chos yongs su gtong ba 'dis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-0: bskal pa grangs med pa gsum gyi yang dag par bsgrub par bya ba'i byang chub yang @42a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-2: snying rje chen pos yongs su bsgos pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs par byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-5: ma 'dres pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gsum dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-6: snying rje chen po dang ldan pa'i yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas spos mchog ces bya bar 'gyur te 'jig rten du 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-7: de'i sbyin par bya ba'i chos ni gang nga la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur pa 'di yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-9: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-10: gang po la sogs pa'i rtogs pa brjod pa brgya pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-12: bdug pa zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-13: sangs rgyas com ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-16: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42a-25: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-0: mi'am ci @42b dang; lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-7: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-8: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-9: de'i tshe mnyan du yod pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-10: tshong dpon gnyis phan tshun mi mthun par gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-11: de gnyis las gcig ni rdzogs byed la dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-12: gcig ni sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la dad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-13: de nas de gnyis phan tshun gtam du bya ba nges par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-14: rdzogs byed kyi dge bsnyen na re /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-15: sangs rgyas pas chos rdzogs byed khyad par du 'phags so zhes zer ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-16: sangs rgyas kyi dge bsnyen na re /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-17: bcom ldan 'das yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ches khyad par du 'phags so zhes zer ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-18: de nas de gnyis kyi bdog pa thams cad yal bar bya ba'i skugs kyi gta' bzhag go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-19: de nas re zhig na rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis thos nas bron po rnams la de gnyis kyi de sbyongs shig ces bsgo'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-20: de nas blon po de dag gis yul thams cad du dril bsgrags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-21: da ste zhag bdun na sangs rgyas dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-22: mu stegs can gyi dge bsnyen gnyis kyi sbyang bar chad kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:42b-23: su rmad du byung ba lta 'dod pa de dag gshegs shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-1: de nas zhag bdun lon pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-2: sa phyogs go skabs yangs pa zhig tu mi 'bum phrag du ma 'dus pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-3: nam mkha' la lha 'bum phrag du ma 'dus pa'i nang du ba lang gi lci bas dkyil 'khor byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-5: me tog phreng thams cad bsdogs pa la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-6: thog ma kho nar mu stegs can gyi dge bsnyen gyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-7: bden pas gsol ba gdab pa byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-9: bden pa'i tshig gang gis rdzogs byed la sogs pa ston pa drug mchog yin pa'i bden pa dang bden pa'i tshig des na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-12: chu 'di de rnams kyi thad du song zhig ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-13: de skad ces brjod pa'i mdo la me tog de dag ni sa la lhags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-15: chu ni sa la thim zhing yongs su zad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-16: yongs su gtugs par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-17: de nas skye bo phal po che de dag gis ca co dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-18: ga zha bton te skad po che phyung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-19: de nas mu stegs can gyi dge bsnyen gyis de mthong nas; cang mi zer bar 'dug la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-20: spa gong zhing phrag pa bcum ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:43a-21: mig phab nas spobs pa med par gyur te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79a-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang rol mo mkhan de dag la cang mi gsung bas gnang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79a-7: de nas rol mo mkhan de dag dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79a-14: gyo mo med par byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79a-15: spos chab kyis chag chag ni btab /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79a-17: bdug pa sna tshogs kyis ni bdugs /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79a-18: me tog gi bla res ni brgyan to //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79a-24: zhal zas bzang pos kyang bcom ldan 'das nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa tshim par byas so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79b-0: 'di ni sangs rgyas @79b bcom ldan 'das gang gi tshe 'dzum pa mdzad pa'i chos nyid de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79b-1: de'i tshe zhal nas 'od zer sngon po dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79b-23: grang ba'i sems can dmyal ba gang yin pa de dag tu ni dro bar gyur te 'bab bo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79b-25: de nas de dag 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79b-29: 'on te gzhan du skyes sam snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79b-30: de nas de dag dad pa bskyed pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das sprul pa 'gyed pa mdzad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79b-31: de dag gis sprul pa mthong nas 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79b-33: bdag cag ni 'di nas kyang shi 'phos par ma gyur la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:79b-34: gzhan du'ang ma skyes mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80a-0: 'on kyang sngon ma byung ba'i sems can snang ba @80a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80a-1: 'di'i mthus bdag cag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to snyam mo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80a-13: tshangs pa chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80a-27: 'og min gyi lha rnams kyi bar du song nas mi rtag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80a-30: bdag med pa'i sgra sgrogs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80a-31: tshigs su bcad pa gnyis kyang rjod par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-0: nges par 'byung ba @80b brtsam par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-1: sangs rgyas bstan la sbyor bar gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-2: 'dam bu'i khyim la glang chen bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-3: 'chi bdag sde ni gzhom par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-5: bag yod spyod par byed pa ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-6: skye ba'i 'khor ba rab spangs nas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-7: sdug bsngal zad par byed par 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-9: de nas 'od zer de dag gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams bskor nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-10: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi phyi bzhin 'brang ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-12: bcom ldan 'das kyi snam logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-19: mir skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-20: pus mo gnyis su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-21: stobs kyi 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-22: phyag g-yon pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:80b-23: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-0: phyag g-yas pa'i mthil du mi snang bar @81a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-2: lhar skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-3: lte bar mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-4: nyan thos kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-5: zhal du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-6: rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-7: smin mtshams kyi mdzod spur mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-8: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-9: dbu'i gtsug tor du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-10: de nas 'od zer de dag gis bcom ldan 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-11: bcom ldan 'das kyi smin mtshams kyi mdzod spur mi snang bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-12: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos thal mo sbyar te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-14: tshon sna stong gis spel ba sna tshogs can //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-15: mang po zhal gyi sgo nas byung bar gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-16: de yis phyogs rnams kun tu snang bar bgyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-17: nyi ma shar bas ji ltar bgyis pa bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-18: yang tshigs su bcad de gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-19: rgod dang bral zhing rgyags dang mi dgyes spangs pa yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-20: sangs rgyas 'gro ba dag gi dam pa'i rgyur gyur pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-21: rgyal ba dgra thub rnams ni rgyu rkyen ma mchis par //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-22: padma'i rtsa dang dung mdog lta bu'i 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-23: brtan pos nyid kyi blo yis dus bab mkhyen lags na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81a-24: dge slong rgyal dbang nyan pa som nyi 'tshal ba rnams //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-0: thub pa khyu mchog gi ni gsung mchog @81b brtan pa dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-1: bzang po dag gis the tshom skyes pa bsal bar gsol //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-2: rgya mtsho dang ni ri rgyal lta bur brtan pa yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-3: mgon po rdzogs sangs rgyas rnams gyin 'da' 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-4: gang gi don du dpa' bo 'dzum pa ston mdzad pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-5: de ni khyod las skye bo phal chen nyan par tshal //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-9: de ni de bzhin te; kun dga' bo /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-10: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams ni rgyu med rkyen med par 'dzum pa mi mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-12: rol mo mkhan 'di dag gis nga la bkur sti 'di lta bu byas pa mthong ngam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-16: rol mo mkhan 'di dag dge ba'i rtsa ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-18: sbyin par bya ba'i chos yongs su gtong ba 'dis dus ji lta ba bzhin du rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub yang dag par bsgrubs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-19: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na skad snyan zhes bya ba'i rang sangs rgyas sha stag tu 'gyur te; sdug cing phongs pa rnams la snying brtse ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-20: bas mtha'i gnas mal gyis 'tsho ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-21: 'jig rten gyi yon gnas gcig pur 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-22: de dag gi sbyin par bya ba'i chos ni gang nga la sems dga' bar gyur ba 'di yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:81b-26: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-1: gang dag gi mthu 'di 'dra bar 'gyur ba de dag gang du mdzad lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-4: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis sngon tshe rabs gzhan dag tu tshogs rnyed cing rkyen grub pa dang ldan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-6: gdon mi za bar 'ong ba'i las de dag byas shing bsags pas na nga nyid kyis las byas shing bsags pa de dag gzhan su zhig gis nyams su myong bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-8: las byas shing bsags pa rnams ni phyi rol gyi sa'i khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-11: rlung gi khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-13: mi dge ba byas shing bsags pa rnams ni zin pa'i phung po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-15: skye mched rnams 'ba' zhig la rnam par smin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-16: lus can dag gi las rnams ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-17: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-18: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-21: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na de bzhin gshegs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-23: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82a-28: skyes bu gdul bya'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-1: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rtogs mdzad ces bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-2: de ljongs rgyu zhing gshegs pa las rgyal po'i pho brang 'khor zhig tu byon to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-3: de nas rgyal po'i skyed mos tshal dus tshigs thams cad du 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa zhig yod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-4: skyed mos tshal der bcom ldan 'das gshegs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-5: rgyal po de la phan gdags pa'i phyir /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-6: shing ljon pa zhig gi drung na rten cing bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-7: de nas gdan bting ba la bzhugs te me'i khams la snyoms par zhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-8: de nas rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba'i rgyal po de bud med kyi sil snyan dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-9: rol mo'i sgra sgrogs pa dag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-10: skyed mos tshal du song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-11: de nas rgyal po de skyed mos tshal de na 'khyam zhing 'gro bas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-12: bcom ldan 'das yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rtogs mdzad mdzes shing dga' bar mdzad pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-15: thugs mchog tu dul zhing rnam par zhi ba dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-16: gser gyi mchod sdong ltar dpal 'bar ba mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-17: mthong nas kyang rgyal po de dga' bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-18: btsun mo'i 'khor dang bcas pas sil snyan rnam pa sna tshogs bsgrags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-19: bcom ldan 'das ting nge 'dzin de las bzhengs su gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-20: zhal zas bzang po'ang gsol nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:82b-21: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu smon lam btab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-2: de'i tshe de'i dus na rgyal por gyur pa gang yin pa de ni nga yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-3: ngas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rtogs mdzad de la mchod pa byas pa de nyid kyi rgyus /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-4: da ltar nga la rol mo mkhan rnams kyis 'di lta bu'i bsnyen bkur byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-6: de bas na 'di ltar bslab par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-7: ston pa la bkur stir bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-11: ston pa la bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-15: brten te gnas par bya'o zhes dge slong dag khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-16: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-17: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-18: mchog sbyin zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-19: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-20: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-22: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83a-30: mi'am ci rnams dang; lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-1: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-8: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-9: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-10: de nas mnyan du yod pa na gzhan gyi chung ma la byi ba byed pa las dri ma can la gnas pa zhig yod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-11: de rgyal po'i mis bzung nas rgyal po'i mis bzung nas rgyal po la phul lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-12: de nas de nyes pa byed byed pa'i phyir rgyal pos gshed ma la gtad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-13: de nas de rgyal po'i mi gos sngon po bgos pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-15: ka ra w'i ra'i me tog gi phreng ba mgul na thogs pa rnams kyis lam po che dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-18: sum mdo rnams su 'o dod bos nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-19: grong khyer gyi lho sgor khrid do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-20: de'i skabs su sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis ni mi mkhyen pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-23: thugs su mi chud pa ci'ang med la; sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-24: 'jig rten la phan 'dogs pa la zhugs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-25: srung ba gcig pa dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-31: rig pa gsum snang bar mdzad pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-32: bslab pa gsum la legs par bslabs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-33: 'dul ba'i gzhi gsum la mkhas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:83b-34: chu bo bzhi las brgal ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:84a-1: 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi'i zhabs kyi mthil shin tu brtan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:84a-2: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi la yun ring po nas 'dris par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:84a-4: khyu mchog gi yang dag pa'i seng ge'i sgra chen po sgrogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:84a-5: yan lag lnga rnam par spangs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:84a-6: 'gro ba lnga las yang dag par 'das pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:84a-7: yan lag drug dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:84a-8: pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs pa; rtag tu gnas par bya ba drug la gnas pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94a-17: padma'i rtsa dang dung mdog lta bu'i 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94a-18: brtan pos nyid kyi blo yis dus bab mkhyen lags na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94a-19: dge sbyong rgyal dbang nyan pa som nyi 'tshal ba rnams //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94a-20: thub pa khyu mchog gi ni gsung mchog brtan pa dang //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-0: mgon po rdzogs sangs rgyas rnams gyin 'da' @94b 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-1: gang gi don du dpa' bo 'dzum pa ston mdzad pa //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-3: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-10: khyim bdag 'dis nga la 'di lta bu'i bkur sti byas pa mthong ngam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-13: khyim bdag 'di dge ba'i rtsa ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-15: sbyin par byas pa'i chos yongs su gtong ba 'dis bskal pa grangs med pa gsum gyis yang dag par bsgrub par bya ba'i byang chub yang dag par bsgrubs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-16: snying rje chen pos yongs su bsgos pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs par byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-19: ma 'dres pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gsum dang; snying rje chen po dang ldan pa'i yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lha'i zas sbyin zhes bya bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-21: de'i sbyin par bya ba'i chos ni gang nga la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur pa 'di yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:94b-22: skabs 'di ma ga dha'i rgyal po gzugs can snying po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-0: g-yog 'khor rnams kyis thos nas mchog tu ya mtshan @95a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-2: de nas dge slong dag the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-3: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-4: bcom ldan 'das khyim bdag 'dis bcom ldan 'das nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa la lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-5: mi'i 'byor pa dag gis mchod pa bgyis pa la gzigs /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-8: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis sngon tshe rabs gzhan dag tu tshogs rnyed cing rkyen grub pa dang ldan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-9: dpa' rgal bzhin du 'byung la gdon mi za bar 'ong ba'i las de dag byas shing bsags pas na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-10: nga nyid kyis las byas shing bsags pa 'di dag gzhan su zhig gis nyams su myong bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-12: las byas shing bsags pa rnams ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-13: phyi rol gyi sa'i khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-16: rlung gi khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-18: mi dge ba byas shing bsags pa rnams ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-21: skye mched rnams 'ba' zhig la rnam par smin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-22: lus can dag gi las rnams ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-23: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95a-24: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-4: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-9: skyes bu gdul bya'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-13: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das gang po zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-14: de nas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang po ljongs rgyu zhing gshegs pa las /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-15: rgyal po'i pho brang 'khor zhig tu byon te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-16: rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba'i rgyal po des yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang po ljongs rgyu zhing gshegs pa las /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-17: rgyal po'i pho brang 'khor der byon to zhes thos so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-18: thos nas kyang rgyal po'i 'byor pa chen po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-19: rgyal po'i mthu chen po dang ldan pas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang po ga la ba der song ste phyin nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-20: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang po'i zhabs la mgo bos phyag btsal te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:95b-23: rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba'i rgyal po de yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang pos byang chub thob par byed pa'i chos rnams yang dag par 'dzin du bcug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-0: de nas rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba'i rgyal po des yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang po nyan @96a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-1: thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa la zla ba gsum gyi bar du na bza' dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-6: sman zong rnams la spyan drangs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-7: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang pos kyang cang mi gsung bas gnang ngo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-9: zla ba gsum gyi bar du na bza' dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-14: sman zong rnams kyis bsnyen bkur byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-15: bcom ldan 'das kyi sku gzugs kyang rin po che las byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-16: sangs rgyas kyi dga' ston byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-17: der srog chags 'bum phrag du ma dad pa chen po skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-19: rkyen des de dag yongs su mya ngan las 'das so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-22: de'i tshe de'i dus na rgyal por gyur pa gang yin pa de ni nga yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-23: ngas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang po la de lta bu'i mchod pa byas pa des na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-24: ngas 'khor ba na bde ba mtha' yas pa nyams su myong ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-25: de nyid kyi rgyus da ltar de bzhin gshegs par gyur pa na'ang nga la tshong dpon dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96a-26: brgya byin gyis 'di lta bu'i mchod pa byas so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-8: mchod pa byas nas brten te gnas par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-9: zhes dge slong khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-10: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-12: gang po la sogs pa rtogs pa brjod pa brgya pa las /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-14: gang po la sogs pa'i rtogs pa brjod pa brgya pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-18: de bzhin 'khor lo mgo bcu pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-20: mnyan pa dang ni spos ngad ldang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-21: dri med gdangs snyan zhes bya ba //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-22: sde tshan dag tu bstan pa yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-24: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-25: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-27: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:96b-36: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-7: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-16: gangg'a'i klung gi 'gram du byon to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-17: de'i tshe gangg'a'i klung gi 'gram nas thag mi ring ba zhig na mchod rten zhig ral du gyur pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-19: nyi tshan gyis bshig pa zhig 'dug pa de dge slong rnams kyis mthong nas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-22: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-23: rang sangs rgyas tsandan zhes bya ba zhig byung ste de'i yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-24: dge slong rnams kyis gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-26: rang sangs rgyas tsandan las byung lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-27: ming ni ci las btags lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-28: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa; dge slong dag /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97a-30: ming ci las btags pa nyan par 'dod dam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-2: 'o na legs par rab tu nyon la yid la zungs shig dang ngas bshad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-4: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-5: grong khyer w'a ra n'a si na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-6: rgyal po tshangs byin zhes bya ba zhig rgyal po byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-12: mi mang pos gang ba dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-24: rgyal po de'ang chos can chos dang ldan pa'i rgyal po chos bzhin du rgyal po byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-25: de bu med nas bu 'dod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-30: tshangs pa la sogs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-31: lha'i khyad par gzhan dag la'ang gsol ba 'debs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-33: kun dga' ra ba'i lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-35: lam gyi bzhi mdo'i lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-37: gtor ma len pa'i lha dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-41: 'jig rten na'ang gsol ba btab pa'i rgyus bu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-42: bu mo skye bar 'gyur ro zhes bya ba'i gtam de yod mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-43: de'ang de lta ni ma yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:97b-44: gal te gsol ba btab pa'i rgyus bu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98a-2: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po bzhin du re re la'ang bu stong stong yod par 'gyur ba'i rigs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98a-3: ye ni gnas gsum tshogs pa las bu dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98a-11: de'ang gsol ba 'debs pa lhur byed cing 'dug la de'i skyed mos tshal gyi rdzing chen po zhig yod pa de'i nang nas kyang padma tshad las 'das par che ba zhig skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98a-12: de nyin gcig bzhin du cher skye la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98a-13: kha ni mi 'bye ba zhig yod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98a-14: de nas kun dga' ra ba'i srung mas rgyal po la gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98a-15: de nas rgyal pos kyang padma de legs par srungs shig ces bsgo'o //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98a-17: padma de'i snying po la khye'u gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa mdog bzang ba gser gyi kha dog can /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-0: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus mdzes par byas pa zhig @98b skyil mo krung bcas shing 'dug ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-2: lus las ni tsandan gyi dri 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-3: de nas kun dga' ra ba'i srung mas kyang rgyal po la gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-4: de nas rgyal po blon po dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-6: khye'u des mthong ma thag tu rgyal po la smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-8: bdag ni khyod sras mi mnga' ba'i sras lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-9: de nas rgyal po dga' zhing mgu la yi rangs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-11: bu; de ni khyod ji skad zer ba bzhin no //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-13: padma'i snying po las khye'u blangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-15: de nas khye'u des gang dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-20: grong khyer gyi mi rnams kyis rgyal po la gsol pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:98b-22: lha; sras tsandan btang ba'i rigs so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-3: de nas de der 'gro ba na gom pa re re la padma lta na sdug cing yid 'phrog pa dag byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-4: de dag la nyi ma'i 'od zer gyis phog ma thag tu rnyis shing bskams so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-5: de nas sems can dag pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-7: sngon sangs rgyas la dge ba'i rtsa ba skyed skyed pa des de mthong nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-8: tshul bzhin du yid la byed pa skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-9: ji ltar padma 'di dag skyes pa'i mod la ni mdzes par 'dug la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-10: nyi ma'i 'od zer gyis gdungs pas ni rnyis shing bskam par 'gyur ba de bzhin du /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-15: de nas re zhig na gnas gtsang ma'i ris kyi lha rnams kyis de la gos tshon can dag phul te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-18: de mthong bas rgyal po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99a-20: grong rdal gyi mi rnams dang bcas par dga' ba chen po thob ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99b-0: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' @99b stsal pa; dge slong dag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99b-1: rang sangs rgyas tsandan ni de las byung ste ming yang de las btags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:99b-2: dge slong rnams kyis sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:101a-17: de nas de dag sprul pa la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur nas /
