K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-18: de'i tshe rgyal po'i khab nas ded dpon zhig rgya mtsho chen po'i nang du zhugs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-19: de'i chung ma lang tshol bab pa de khyim thab la gdung zhing yongs su mi chad la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-21: de'i khyim thab ma 'ongs nas des sred med kyi bu la phyag btsal te dam bcas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-22: gal te bdag gi khyim thab myur du 'ongs na bdag gis khyod la gser gyi 'khor lo dbul lo zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-23: de nas de'i khyim thab rgya mtsho'i nang nas myur du phyir 'khor te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-24: nye zho med par bde bar 'ongs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-25: de nas des gser gyi 'khor lo byed du bcug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-26: de bran po'i tshogs kyis bskor bas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-30: me tog khyer te lha khang du chas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:103b-31: de'i skabs su sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis ni mi mkhyen ba'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-0: @104a *// thugs su mi chud pa ci'ang med la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-1: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-2: 'jig rten la phan 'dogs pa la zhugs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-3: srung ba gcig pa dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-9: rig pa gsum snang bar mdzad pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-10: bslab pa gsum la legs par bslabs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-11: 'dul ba'i gzhi gsum la mkhas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-12: chu bo bzhi las brgal ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-13: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi'i zhabs kyi mthil shin tu brtan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-14: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi la yun ring po nas 'dris par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-16: khyu mchog gi yang dag pa'i seng ge'i sgra chen po sgrogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-17: yan lag lnga rnam par spangs pa; 'gro ba lnga las yang dag par 'das pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-18: yan lag drug dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-19: pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs par byed pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-20: rtag tu gnas par bye ba drug la gnas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-21: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun gyi me tog gis phyug pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-22: lam yan lag brgyad pa ston pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-23: mthar gyis snyoms par 'jug pa dgu la mkhas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-24: stobs bcu'i stobs dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-25: phyogs bcur grags pas kun tu rgyas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104a-26: brgya phrag bcu la dbang byed pa bas kyang ches khyad par du 'phags pa rnams ni chos nyid kyis nyin dus gsum /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-0: mtshan dus gsum @104b du sangs rgyas kyi spyan gyis 'jig rten la gzigs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-4: su ni nyam nga bar gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-5: su ni gnod pa dang ldan /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-9: su ni ngan song du gzhol /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-11: su ni ngan song du bab /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-12: su ni ngas ngan song nas phyung ste mtho ris dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-15: su ni 'dod pa'i 'dam du bying ba las lag nas drang bar bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-16: su ni 'phags pa'i nor bdun med pa las 'phags pa'i nor bdun gyi dbang phyug la dbang byed du gzhug par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-17: su ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams ma bskyed pa las bskyed par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-18: su ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams bskyed zin pa las yongs su smin par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-19: su ni yongs su smin zin pa las rnam par grol bar bya snyam du ye shes gzigs pa 'jug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-21: rgya mtsho chu srin rnams kyi gnas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-22: dus rlabs yel bar 'gyur yang srid //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-23: gdul bar bya ba'i sras rnams la //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-24: sangs rgyas dus las yol ba med //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-25: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi bu mo des nga mthong na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-26: rang byang chub kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba bskyed par 'gyur ro snyam du gzigs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-27: de nas bcom ldan 'das snga dro sham thabs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:104b-29: lhung bzed bsnams nas dge slong gi tshogs kyis zham ring byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-0: dge slong gi dge 'dun gyis mdun du bdar nas rgyal po'i khab tu @105a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-2: de nas bu mo des sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das sku skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis brgyan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-3: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus mdzad par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-5: nyi ma stong bas lhag pa'i 'od mnga' ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-6: rin po che'i ri bo 'gro ba lta bu kun nas bzang ba mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-7: de nas mthong ba'i mod la dga' ba thob ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-8: bcom ldan 'das la gser gyi 'khor lo dor bar byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-9: de nas bran mos bkag ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-10: 'di sred med kyi bu ma yin no zhes byas so; ;'on kyang de bkag bzhin du dad pa drag pos yid 'dun par gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-11: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis steng du gser gyi 'khor lo bor ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-15: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'dzum pa mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-16: 'di ni sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams gang gi tshe 'dzum pa mdzad pa'i chos nyid de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-17: de'i tshe zhal nas 'od zer sngon po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105a-23: 'og tu 'gro ba gang yin pa de dag ni sems can dmyal ba yang sos dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-6: autpa la ltar gas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-8: padma ltar gas pa chen por song nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-9: tsha ba'i sems can dmyal ba gang yin pa de dag tu ni bsil bar gyur te 'bab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-10: grang ba'i sems can dmyal ba gang yin pa de dag tu ni dro bar gyur te 'bab bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-11: de nas sems can de dag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-12: de nas de dag 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-13: kye; ci; bdag cag 'di nas shi 'phos sam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-14: 'o na te gzhan du skyes sam snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-15: de nas de dag dad pa bskyed pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das sprul pa 'gyed par mdzad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-16: de dag gis sprul pa mthong nas 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-17: kye; bdag cag ni 'di nas shi 'phos par ma gyur la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-18: gzhan du'ang ma skyes mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-19: 'on kyang sngon ma byung ba'i sems can snang ba 'di'i mthus /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-20: bdag cag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-21: de nas de dag sprul pa la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-22: sems can dmyal ba myong bar 'gyur ba'i las de zad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:105b-23: lha dang; mi rnams kyi nang du gang du bden pa rnams kyi snod du rung bar 'gyur ba der nyid mtshams 'dzin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-0: steng du 'gro ba gang yin pa de dag ni rgyal chen bzhi'i ris @106a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-2: sum cu rtsa gsum pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-8: tshangs pa'i mdun na 'don pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-9: tshangs pa chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-23: 'og min gyi lha rnams kyi bar du song nas mi rtag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-26: bdag med pa'i sgra sgrogs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-27: tshigs su bcad pa gnyis kyang rjod par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-28: nges par 'byung ba brtsam par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-29: sangs rgyas bstan la sbyor bar gyis; ;'dam bu'i khyim la glang chen bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-30: 'chi bdag sde ni gzhom par gyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-32: bag yod spyod par byed pa ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-33: skye ba'i 'khor ba rab spangs nas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-34: sdug bsngal zad par byed par 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106a-36: de nas 'od zer de dag gis stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams bskor nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-0: @106b bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi phyi bzhin 'brang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-1: gal te bcom ldan 'das kyis 'das pa'i las lung sten par bzhad na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-2: bcom ldan 'das kyi snam logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-3: ma 'ongs pa'i las lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-4: mdun logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-5: sems can dmyal bar skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-6: zhabs kyi mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-7: dud 'gro skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-8: zhabs kyi rting par mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-9: yi dvags su skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-10: zhabs kyi mthe bor mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-11: mir skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-12: pus mo gnyis su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-13: stobs kyi 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni; phyag g-yon pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-14: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-15: phyag g-yas pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-16: lhar skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-17: lte bar mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-18: nyan thos kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-19: zhal du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-20: rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-21: smin mtshams kyi mdzod spur mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:106b-22: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-0: dbu'i gtsug tor du mi snang bar 'gyur @107a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-1: ro; ;de nas 'od zer de dag gis bcom ldan 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyi smin mtshams kyi mdzod spur mi snang bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-3: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos thal mo sbyar te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-5: tshon sna stong gis spel ba sna tshogs can //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-6: mang po zhal gyi sgo nas byung bar gyur; ;de yis phyogs rnams kun tu snang bar bgyis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-7: nyi ma shar bas ji ltar bgyis pa bzhin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-8: yang tshigs su bcad de gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-9: rgod dang bral zhing rgyags dang mi dgyes spangs pa yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-10: sangs rgyas 'gro ba dag gi dam pa'i rgyur gyur pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-11: rgyal pa dgra thub rnams ni rgyu rkyen ma mchis par //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-12: padma'i rtsa dang dung mdog lta bu'i 'dzum mi ston; ;brtan pos nyid kyi blo yis dus bab mkhyen lags na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-13: dge slong rgyal dbang nyan pa so ma nyi 'tshal ba rnams //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-14: thub pa khyu mchog gi ni gsung mchog brtan pa dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-15: bzang po bdag gis the tshom skyes pa bsal bar gsol //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-16: rgya mtsho dang ni ri rgyal lta bur brtan pa yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-17: mgon po rdzogs sangs rgyas rnams gyin 'da' 'dzum mi ston //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-18: gang gi don du dpa' bo 'dzum pa ston mdzad pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-19: de ni khyod las skye ba phal chen nyan par 'tshal //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107a-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-2: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams ni rgyu med rkyen med par 'dzum pa mi mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-4: bu mo 'dis de bzhin gshegs pa la gser gyi 'khor lo bar ba mthong ngam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-8: bu mo 'di dge ba'i rtsa ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-10: sbyin par bya ba'i chos yongs su gtong ba 'dis bskal pa bco lnga'i bar du log par ltung bar mi 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-12: mi'i bde ba nyams su myong nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-13: rang sangs rgyas 'khor lo bla ma zhes bya bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-14: de'i sbyin par bya ba'i chos ni gang nga la sems dga' bar gyur pa 'di yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-16: de bas na 'di ltar bslab par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-19: nyan thos rnams la bkur sti bya'o zhes dge slong khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-21: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-22: mgo bcu pa zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-23: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-24: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:107b-26: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-1: dang; lha ma yin rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-4: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-14: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-21: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-22: yul ma ga dha na ljongs rgyu zhing gshegs pa las gangg'a'i klung gi 'gram du byon to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-23: de nas dge slong rnams kyis thag ring po zhig nas mchod rten rnying pa rlung dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-24: nyi tshan gyis bshig pa zhig 'dug pa de mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-25: mthong nas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-28: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-29: rang sangs rgyas mgo bcu pa'i yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-30: dge slong rnams kyis gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-32: rang sangs rgyas mgo bcu pa ga las byung lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-33: ming ni ci las btags lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-34: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108a-35: dge slong dag khyed rang sangs rgyas mgo bcu pa ga las byung ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-0: ming @108b ce las btags pa nyan par 'dod dam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-7: legs par rab tu nyon la yid la zungs shig dang ngas bshad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-9: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-10: grong khyer w'a ra n'a si na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-11: rgyal po tshangs pas byin zhes bya ba zhig rgyal po byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-17: mi mang pos gang ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-23: mu ge dang; nad rnams med pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-27: ma he dang ldan par 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-28: rgyal po de'ang chos can chos dang ldan pa'i rgyal po zhig ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-29: chos bzhin du rgyal po byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-30: de nas rgyal po de bu med nas bu 'dod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-35: tshangs pa la sogs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-36: lha'i khyad par gzhan dag la yang gsol ba 'debs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-38: kun dga' ra ba'i lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-40: lam gyi bzhi mdo'i lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-42: gtor ma len pa'i lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:108b-45: rtag tu phyi bzhin 'brang ba'i lha rnams la'ang gsol ba 'debs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-3: bu mo skye bar 'gyur ro zhes bya ba'i gtam de yod mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-4: de'ang de lta ni ma yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-5: gal te gsol ba btab pa'i rgyus bu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-6: bu mo skye bar 'gyur du zin na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-7: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po bzhin du re re la'ang bu stong stong yod par 'gyur ba'i rigs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-8: ye ni gnas gsum tshogs pa las bu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-11: pha ma gnyis 'dod chags langs te phrad pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-12: ma dus la bab cing zla mtshan dang ldan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-14: gnas 'di gsum tshogs ba las bu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-16: de'ang gsol ba 'debs pa lhur byed cing 'dug la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-17: de'i skyed mos tshal gyi rdzing chen po autpa la dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-23: zel mo la sogs pa bya sna tshogs kyis mdzes par byas ba zhig yod pa de'i nang nas kyang padma tshad las 'das par che ba zhig glo tol du skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-24: de nyin gcig bzhin du cher skye la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-25: kha ni mi 'bye ba zhig yod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-26: de nas kun dga' ra ba'i srung mas rgyal po la gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-27: de nas rgyal pos kyang padma de legs par srungs shig ces bsgo'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109a-28: phyis re zhig na nyi ma 'char kar padma de kha bye nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-0: padma de'i snying po la khye'u gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa @109b mdog bzang ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-8: lus skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis legs par brgyan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-9: dbe byad bzang po brgyad cus mdzes par byas pa zhig skyil mo krung bcas shing 'dug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-10: kun dga' ra ba'i srung mas kyang rgyal po la gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-11: de nas rgyal pos thos nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-13: btsun mo dang bcas pa skyed mos tshal du dong ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-14: padma'i snying po la de lta bur mdzes shig 'dug pa mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-15: mthong nas kyang dga' zhing mgu la rab tu dga' ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-16: yi rangs nas dga' ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-18: rdzing gi nang du zhugs nas khye'u de blangs te bkur sti chen po dang ldan pas rang gi pho brang du khyer nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-21: mtshan mkhan dag la bsnyad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-22: zhag bdun gsum nyi shu rtsa gcig gi bar du btsas ston rgyas par byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-23: mgo bcu pa zhes ming btags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-24: de nas khye'u mgo bcu pa bang na 'tsho ba'i ma ma gnyis dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-25: nu ma snun pa'i ma ma gnyis dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-26: dri ma 'khru ba'i ma ma gnyis dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-27: rtse ba'i ma ma gnyis te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-28: ma ma brgyad la gtad nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:109b-29: de ma ma brgyad kyis 'o ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:110a-0: yo byad kyi khyad par bzang ngo @110a *//

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-2: sor phreng ni zhe sdang gi rgya mtshor lhung ba las bsgral /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-3: bram ze'i bu nga rgyal gyis khengs pa ni nga rgyal gyi mtshor lhung ba las bsgral /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-4: lteng rgyas 'od srung ni gti mug gi rgya mtshor lhung ba las bsgral te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-5: 'on kyang ngas gru btsas ma blangs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-6: de skad ces bka' stsal kyang bsgral bar khas ma blangs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-7: de nas mnyan pa zhig gis bcom ldan 'das kyi gsung yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'ang thos /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-8: gzugs phun sum tshogs pa de'ang mthong nas dad pa skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-9: bdag gis bcom ldan 'das nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa bsgral bar 'tshal lo zhes gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-10: de nas dge slong rnams gyur zhugs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-11: bcom ldan 'das rdzu 'phrul gyis mnyan pa de bas kyang ches sngar pha rol gyi 'gram du zhugs par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-12: de nas mnyan pa des rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul de mthong nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-13: sems dga' bar gyur te zhabs la mgo bos phyag btsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis de la 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi rtogs par 'gyur ba de lta bu'i chos bstan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-15: mnyan pa des de thos nas 'jig tshogs la lta ba'i ri'i rtse mo mthon po nyi shu ye shes kyi rdo rjes bcom nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:120b-16: rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu mngon sum du byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-0: des bden pa mthong nas dga' @121a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-1: ba'i tshig lan gsum du brjod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-3: bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag gi khrag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-4: mchi ma'i rgya mtsho bskams pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-5: rus pa'i ri la bsgral ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-6: ngan song gi sgo thams cad bcad pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-8: thar pa'i sgo rnams phye ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-10: mi rnams kyi nang nas bzhag pa 'di lta bu ni bdag la phas kyang ma bgyis; mas kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-12: lha rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-14: gnyen gyi tshogs kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-15: sngon gyi mtshun rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-17: bram ze rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis lags so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-22: mya ngan 'das pa'i lam yang bdag gis thob //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-25: bdag ni sdug bsngal rgya mtsho pha rol brgal //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121a-29: srid pa stong du mthong bar dka' ba las //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121b-30: des na sems can de dag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121b-31: de nas de dag 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:121b-32: kye; ci; bdag cag ni 'di nas shi 'phos sam /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122a-1: pa bskyed pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das sprul pa 'gyed par mdzad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122a-2: de dag gis sprul pa mthong nas 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122a-3: kye; bdag cag ni 'di nas kyang shi 'phos par ma gyur la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122a-4: gzhan du'ang ma skyes mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122a-5: 'on kyang sngon ma byung ba'i sems can snang ba 'di'i mthus /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122a-6: bdag cag gi gnod pa'i khyad par rnams rtse zhil bar gyur to snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122a-7: de nas de dag sprul pa la sems mngon par dga' bar gyur nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122b-18: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi phyi bzhin 'brang ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122b-26: zhabs kyi rting par mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122b-27: yi dvags su skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:122b-28: zhabs kyi mthe bor mi snang bar 'gyur ro /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:123a-17: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos thal mo sbyar te bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:160b-15: dpe byad bzang po brgyad bcu [?] mdzes par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:160b-17: nyi ma stong bas lhag pa'i 'od mnga' ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:160b-18: rin po che'i ri bo 'gro ba lta bu kun nas bzang ba mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:160b-19: mthong nas kyang dga' bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:160b-20: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la mgo bos phyag btsal nas chos mnyan pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:160b-21: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis de la 'khor ba las skyo bar 'gyur ba'i chos bstan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:160b-22: de thos pas 'khor ba la nyes par lta ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:160b-23: mya ngan las 'das pa la yon tan du lta bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:160b-24: pha ma gnyis kyis gnang nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-1: ldan 'das kyi bstan pa la rab tu byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-2: de de ltar rab tu byung nas nye du de dag dang lhan cig tu 'du zhing gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-3: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis de khyim pa dang 'du ba las bzlog nas dgon par gnas pa la 'dzud par mdzad na de der mi dga'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-4: de nas de bcom ldan 'das kyis lan gsum gyi bar du khyim pa dang 'du ba las bzlog par mdzad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-5: bu; khyim pa dang 'du ba 'di ni nyes pa du ma dang ldan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-6: mig gis shes par bya ba'i gzugs sdug pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-13: rna bas shes par bya ba'i sgra rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-14: snas shes par bya ba'i dri rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-15: lces shes par bya ba'i ro rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-16: lus kyis shes par bya ba'i reg bya rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-23: tsher ma dang 'dra ba dag yod do zhes gsungs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-24: gang du gnas bcas na dge ba'i chos rnams 'phel bar 'gyur ba'i dgon pa'i yon tan dag kyang rnam grangs du mar bsngags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-25: de nas re zhig na rigs kyi bu des dge ba'i bshes gnyen bcom ldan 'das la brten nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161a-26: dgon par gnas pa la'ang rtag tu brtson pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-0: @161b 'bad pas phol mig lnga pa'i 'khor ba'i 'khor lo 'di nyid g-yo zhing mi brtan par rig nas 'du byed kyi rnam pa thams cad rnyil ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-3: rnam par 'jig pa'i chos can yin par rtsad chod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-4: nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs nas dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-5: dgra bcom pa khams gsum pa'i 'dod chags dang bral bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-6: gser dang bong bar mnyam pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-7: nam mkha' dang lag mthil du 'dra ba'i sems dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-8: tsandan spangs pa lta bur bsil bar gyur pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-9: rig pas sgo nga'i sbubs bcom pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-12: so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-15: bkur sti la mi blta ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-17: nye dbang dang bcas pa'i lha rnams kyis mchod cing rjed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-18: gus par smra ba'i gnas su gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-19: de nas des sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis shin tu dka' ba spyod pa'ang mthong nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-21: bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du song ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-22: gus pa dang bcas pas bstod cing ri mo byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-23: de nas dge slong rnams the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-24: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-26: bcom ldan 'das kyis rigs kyi bu 'di lan gsum gyi bar du grong nas bzlog ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-27: dgon pa'i gnas la btsud pa nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:161b-28: dgra bcom pa nyid kyi bar du bzhag pa la gzigs /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-3: da ltar de bzhin gshegs pa 'dod chags dang bral ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-6: skye ba dang; rga ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-13: 'khrug pa rnams las yongs su grol ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-15: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-17: shes bya thams cad la mnga' brnyes zin pa'i tshe rigs kyi bu 'di lan gsum gyi bar du grong nas bzlog ste dgon pa'i gnas la btsud pa nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-18: dgra bcom pa nyid kyi bar du bzhag pa 'di lta la ngo mtshar che ba ci yod /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-19: 'das pa'i dus na 'dod chags dang bcas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-30: 'khrugs pa rnams las yongs su ma grol ba'i tshe'ang ngas rang gi srog yongs su btang nas rigs kyi bu 'di grong nas bzlog ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-31: dgon pa'i gnas la btsud pa de legs par rab tu nyon la yid la zungs shig dang ngas bshad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-33: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162a-34: ri'i sul chu 'bab cing me tog dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-0: rdo gu phun @162b sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa zhig na drang srong dka' thub drag po spyod pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-4: ri dvags kyi g-yang gzhi dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-6: me'i sbyin sreg byed pa zhig 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-7: drang srong de'i mdza' bo'ang ri bong mi'i skad shes pa zhig yod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-8: de nyin gcig bzhin du drang srong gi thad du dus gsum du 'gro'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-9: der song nas gus par smra ba byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-10: gtam rnam pa sna tshogs kyis yang dag par dga' bar byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-11: de gnyis phyir zhing mdza' bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-13: phyis re zhig na than chen byung nas des chu klung dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-14: khron pa rnams chu chung bar gyur la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-15: shing rnams kyang me tog dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-17: de nas drang srong de gnas de na bza' ba med pas mi dga' nas des ri dvags kyi g-yang gzhi dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-18: shin shun rnams kyang brtul to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-19: de nas ri bong des de lta bur gyur pa mthong nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-20: drang srong chen po gar bzhud ces dris so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-23: der btsos pa'i slong mos 'tsho bar bya'o zhes zer ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-24: de nas des drang srong gi tshig thos nas gdung bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-25: pha dang bral ba tsam du bsams nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-26: drang srong de'i rkang pa la phyag btsal te smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:162b-28: gcig tu na khyim gyi gnas ni nyes pa du mas gang la dgon pa'i gnas ni yon tan phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa lags so zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-0: de skad lan du ma byas kyang de ldog @163a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-2: de nas ri bong gis smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-3: gal te mi 'gror mi rung na'ang deng tsam gzhes la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-4: sang gar dgyes par bzhung cig ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-5: de nas drang srong de 'di snyam du sems te; dud 'gro'i skye gnas su skyes pa 'di dag ni sdug cing gsog pa la sred pas na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-6: 'dis ni bdag deng kha zas sna 'ga' zhig la g-yar 'dren par 'dod gor ma chag snyam ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-7: des de la khas blangs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-8: de nas nyin par gyi bya ba byas zin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-9: dro la bab ba na ri bong 'ongs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-10: drang srong de la bskor ba byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-13: gang bdag gis dud 'gro'i skye gnas su skyes pas bya mi bya mi shes nas khyod la cung zad nongs pa ci bgyis pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-14: bdag la khyod kyis bzod pa mdzod cig ces smras nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-15: tsham tshom med par me'i nang du mchongs so; ;de nas drang srong de mi dga' bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-17: bu gcig pa sdug pa la bya ba bzhin du la gor du blangs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-18: bu 'di ci byed ces smras so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-21: dgon pa'i dga' bas bdag gi sha gsol la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-22: zhag gcig gi bar du 'tsho bar mdzod cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-24: nags khung dag tu skyes pa'i ri bong la //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-25: sran sde'u til dang 'bras rnams ci ma mchis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-26: bdag gi lus 'di zhugs la sgrol mdzod la //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-27: gsol te deng tsam dka' thub tshal du bzhugs //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163a-28: de nas drang srong des ri bong gi tshig thos nas mi dga' bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-0: smras @163b ba; gal te de lta na khyod snying du sdug pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-1: dgo na pa snying du sdug pa'i phyir 'di nyid du srog bor yang bla yi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-2: grong du ni bdag mi 'gro'o zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-3: de nas ri bong gis tshig de thos nas sems dga' bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-4: nam mkha' la gyen du bltas nas gsol ba btab ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-5: bdag ni dgon par song nas kyang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-6: dben pa la ni yid dga' na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-7: de yi bden pa'i tshig gis na; ;dbang chen char ni 'bab par shog /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-9: de skad ces smras ma thag tu byang chub sems dpa'i mthus dbang chen gyi gnas kun tu g-yos so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-10: lha rnams ni 'og tu shes pa'i mthong ba 'jug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-11: ci las gyur snyam pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-12: byang chub sems dpa'i mthu yin bar mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-13: de nas re zhig na lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis gnas mal der dbang chen gyi char phab nas phyir yang rtsva dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-17: 'bras bu phun sum tshogs par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-18: de nas drang srong des dge ba'i bshes gnyen ri bong la brten nas; de na gnas bzhin du mngon par shes pa lnga mngon sum du byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-19: de nas drang srong des ri bong la smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-23: snying rje ba'i rang bzhin 'dis ci zhig bsgrub par sems /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:163b-25: 'jig rten long ba 'dren pa med cing yongs su 'dren pa med par sems can ma brgal ba rnams sgrol ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-0: @164a *// dbugs ma phyin pa rnams 'byin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-1: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan las zlo ba'i sangs rgyas su gyur cig ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-2: de nas drang srong des tshig de thos nas ri bong la smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-3: gang gi tshe khyod sangs rgyas su gyur pa de'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-4: bdag kyang dran par gyis shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-10: de'i tshe de'i dus na ri bong du gyur pa gang yin pa de ni nga yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-11: drang srong ni rigs kyi bu 'di kho na nyid yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-12: dge slong dag ;de bas na 'di ltar bslab par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-15: dge ba'i rten dang gnas par bya yi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-18: sdig pa'i rten dang gnas par mi bya'o zhes dge slong khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-19: de nas bcom ldan 'das la tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-21: 'dir bdag gcig pu dben par mchis nas nang du yang dag 'jog la zhugs pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-22: sems la 'di lta bu'i sems kyi yongs su rtog pa byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164a-26: dge ba'i rten 'di ni tshangs par spyod pa'i phyed lags kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-0: sdig @164b pa'i rten ni de lta ma lags so snyam bgyid do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-1: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-9: sdig pa'i rten ni de lta ma yin no zhes ma zer zhig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-14: dge ba'i rten 'di ni tshangs par spyod pa ril po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-18: yongs su byang ba yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-21: sdig pa'i rten ni de lta ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-24: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la brten nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-25: sems can skye ba'i chos can rnams skye ba'i chos can las yongs su grol bar 'gyur ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-33: 'khrug pa'i chos can rnams rga ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:164b-39: 'khrug pa'i chos can las yongs su grol bar 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165a-0: de bas na rnam grangs 'di kho nas khyod kyis 'di ltar rig par @165a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165a-5: dge ba'i rten 'di ni tshangs par spyod pa ril po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165a-9: yongs su byang ba yin gyi /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165a-15: chos tshol zhes bya ba ni /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165a-17: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165a-19: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165a-27: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165a-37: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165b-0: zhal zas @165b dang; gzims cha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165b-4: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165b-6: bcom ldan 'das blta ba'i phyir song nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165b-7: rang gis lag dar te rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal 'phyag par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165b-8: de nas phyi zhig na khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin la brel bzhig byung ngo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:165b-19: nyan thos chen po rnams kyis rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal phyags nas mdun khang du gshegs te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:166a-3: lha rnams mgu bar 'gyur ba dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:166b-16: yang dag par dga' bar mdzad nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:166b-21: bcom ldan 'das chos la zhes skyes shing gus pa skyes te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:168a-7: de btsas pa'i tshe btsas ston byas nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:168a-18: ma ma brgyad kyis 'o ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:168a-24: yo byad kyi khyad par bzang ngo cog gis bskyed bsrings te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:168b-1: 'dzam bu gling thams cad du gser bye ba bstan kyang legs par gsungs pa ma rnyed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:168b-2: de nas de dag gis rgyal po la gsol so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:168b-3: de nas rgyal po de legs par gsungs pa nyan par 'dod pa'i phyir gdung zhing yi chad do //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:169a-0: gal te der bdag nyid kyis mchong sbyod na ni de'i 'og @169a *//

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:169b-8: gnod sbyin gyi gzugs mi snang bar byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:169b-9: rang gi gzugs su 'dug nas tshigs su bcad pa smras pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:169b-19: rgyal po'i pho brang 'khor kun tu bskor to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:169b-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:169b-23: de'i tshe de'i dus na rgyal por gyur pa gang yin pa de ni nga yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:169b-24: de'i tshe'ang ngas legs par gsungs pa mnyan pa'i phyir rang gi srog yongs su btang na da ltar lta ci smos /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:169b-26: de bas na 'di ltar bslab par bya'o chos la bkur stir bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170a-2: mchod pa byas nas brten te gnas par bya'o zhes dge slong khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170a-3: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170a-7: blon po chen po rnams dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170a-33: sman zong rnams brnyes pa; nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170b-0: de nas bcom ldan 'das @170b snga dro sham thabs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170b-2: lhung bzed bsnams nas mnyan du yod par bsod snyoms la gshegs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170b-3: de nas re zhig na mthar gyis gshegs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170b-4: lam po cher zhugs pa dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170b-14: bdag la k'arsh'a pa n'a lnga brgya ma stsal gyi bar du khyod kyis ri mo 'di mi 'da' bar gsol /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170b-19: de nas ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis thos ma thag tu blon po'i tshogs kyis zham ring byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170b-20: bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:170b-21: bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:171a-4: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-6: kun tu rgyu rab bzang 'di ni legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu byung ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-7: bsnyen par rdzogs shing dge slong gi dngos por 'gyur bar 'tshal lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-8: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis kun tu rgyu rab bzang la bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-10: tshangs par spyad pa spyod cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-11: de nas de nyid kyis tshe dang ldan pa de rab tu byung bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-12: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'ang de yin la dge slong gi dngos po'ang de yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-13: de ltar rab tu byung nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-14: tshe dang ldan pa de gcig pu dben par 'dug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-15: bag yod cing brtun la bcum nas gnas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:176b-16: gang gi phyir rigs kyi bu dag skra dang kha spu bregs nas gos tshon can bgos te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-0: yang dag par dad pa kho nas khyim nas khyim med par rab tu 'byung bar byed pa'i tshangs par spyod pa bla na med pa'i mthar thug pa de tshe 'di nyid la rang gi mngon par shes pas mngon sum du byas nas bsgrubs te @177a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-1: khong du chud la bdag gi skye ba ni zad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-2: tshangs par spyod pa ni spyad zin to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-4: 'di la srid pa gzhan mi shes so snyam du kun shes par gyur nas; tshe dang ldan pa de dgra bcom par gyur te sems rnam par grol lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-5: de nas tshe dang ldan pa rab bzang dgra bcom pa thob ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-6: rnam par grol ba'i dga' ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-7: bde ba nyams su myong nas 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-8: bdag gis ston pa yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba mthong bar bya ba ni bdag gi cha ma yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-9: de bas ches sngar bdag yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar bya gor ma chag snyam nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-10: der tshe dang ldan pa rab bzang ches sngar yongs su mya ngan las 'das nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-11: de'i 'og tu bcom ldan 'das mya ngan las 'das so; ;gang gi tshe bcom ldan 'das gzims mal gyi tha mar bzhugs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-12: gnad la gnod pa'i tshor ba myong zhing gnad rnams 'chad la tshigs rnams 'bye ba na rab bzang dgra bcom pa nyid la bzhag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-13: grong khyer ku sha'i gyad yul ba mang po chos la btsud pa de'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-14: dge slong dag the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-15: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177a-17: kun tu rgyur ba bzang 'di bcom ldan 'das gnad rnams 'chad cing tshigs rnams 'bye ba na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-0: 'khor ba'i spu gu las bkrol @177b te; gzha' gsang gi mthar thug pa'i grub pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-1: bde ba mya ngan las 'das pa la bzhag pa ni ngo mtshar lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-4: da ltar nga 'dod chags dang bral ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-15: 'khrug pa rnams las yongs su grol ba'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-16: ngas kun tu rgyu rab bzang 'khor ba'i spu gu las bkrol nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-17: gzha' gsang gi mthar thug pa'i grub pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-18: bde ba mya ngan las 'das pa la bzhag pa 'di lta la ngo mtshar che ba ci yod /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-19: 'das pa'i dus na 'dod chags dang bcas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-30: 'khrug pa rnams las yongs su ma grol ba na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-31: bya mi bya mi shes pa'i dud 'gro'i skye gnas su skyes pa'i tshe'ang nas rang gi srog yongs su btang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:177b-32: kun tu rgyu rab bzang dang; grong khyer ku sha'i gyad yul ba rnams 'jigs pa las 'jigs pa med pa la bkod pa de lags par rab tu nyon la yid la zungs shig dang ngas bshad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-1: dag ;sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-2: ri'i sul zhig na ri dvags kyi khyu'i gtso bo ri dvags stong phrag du ma'i 'khor dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-3: mkhas shing gsal la yid gzhungs pa zhig 'dug pa las /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-4: ri dvags kyi khyu de rngon pas bya ra byas nas rgyal po la gsol to //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-6: ri dvags kyi khyu de dag thams cad khongs su bcug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-7: de nas khyu'i gtso bo de 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-8: gal te bdag gis 'di rnams dam bsrungs na ni /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-10: de nas khyu'i gtso bos kho ra khor yug tu bltas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-11: ri dvags kyi tshogs 'di dag phyogs gang logs nas thar bar 'gyur zhig gu snyam mo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178a-13: chu klung de'ang shugs drag cing drag tu khyer bar byed pa zhig yin la /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178b-4: rus pa'i lhag ma tsam zhig lus par zad de /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178b-11: de ri dvags kyi tshogs de dag brgal zin par mthong nas 'chi khar smon lam btab pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178b-12: ji ltar bdag gis ri dvags 'di rnams dang; ri dvags kyi phru gu 'di srog phangs pa bskyabs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178b-13: phongs pa las skyabs byas pa de bzhin du bdag ma 'ongs pa'i dus na bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa na yang 'khor ba'i sbu gu las thar bar byed par gyur cig ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178b-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:178b-18: ri dvags rnams ni grong khyer ku sha'i gyad yul pa 'di rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:179a-0: ri dvags kyi phru gu de ni rab bzang 'di @179a *//

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:179a-20: skye mched rnams 'ba' zhig la rnam par smin par 'gyur ro //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:180a-22: mya ngan med kyis smras pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:197b-0: gser dang bod @197b par mnyam pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:197b-1: nam mkha' dang lag mthil du 'dra ba'i sems dang ldan pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:197b-12: des chu klung gangg'a'i 'gram du lo ma'i spyil po byas te bsam gtan byed do //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:197b-19: tshe dang ldan pa chu smad kyi thad du song nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:197b-21: 'di kho na 'dra ba khyod su zhig /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:197b-24: byams pa'i ma ni bdag yin te //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:197b-25: zas dang skom dang bral ba yi; ;yi dvags rnams kyi nang du skyes //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:197b-26: bdag ni shi ba'i dus 'das nas //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:197b-28: chu yi bag kyang ma mthong na //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-5: btsun pa'i shing drung bde ba lags //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-6: khyod kyi snod nang chu yang bsil //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-7: bkren pa bdag la thugs rje skyed //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-8: skom gyis gdungs kyi chab stsol cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-9: de nas chu smad kyis ma la smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-11: khyod mir gyur pa'i tshe bdag gis sbyin pa dag sbyin zhing bsod nams dag byed du ma bcug gam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-14: bdag ni ser snas non pas sbyin pa dag kyang ma byin bsod nams dag kyang ma byas te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-16: bu gcig de bas na dad pa dris la bdag gi phyir sangs rgyas la sogs pa dge slong gi dge 'dun bshos gsol nas yon gyi rabs 'don par gsol cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-17: 'on tang bdag yi dvags kyi skye gnas nas thar kyang srid do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-20: khyod kyang gral dpon gyi mdun du 'dug cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-23: bdag ni gcer bur 'dug pas ngo tsha ste ngos mi thub bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-26: khyod gang gi tshe sdig pa byed pa de'i tshe ngo mi tsha na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198a-27: da ltar 'bras bu myong ba'i tshe ci'i phyir ngo tsha /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198b-0: de nas chu smad kyis @198b nye du rnams kyi khyim khyim du dad pa dris nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198b-15: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis gzhi de las brten nas yi dvags mo de dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198b-18: yi dvags mo de 'ang sems dga' bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:198b-19: shi nas yi dvags rdzu 'phrul chen mor skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-0: tshe dang ldan pa chu smad kyis yang yi dvags rdzu 'phrul @199a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-1: chen mor skyes par shes so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-9: chags pa'i mun pas mig ni rab bsgribs te //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-11: khyod kyi rus bu chen po sha med pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-12: rus pa pags pa skyi rnams da dung 'dug /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-14: de nas tshe dang ldan pa chu smad kyis lan mang du spyos nas smras pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-15: de'i 'og tu de las ras zung gcig thob bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-16: de nas chu smad kyis dge 'dun la phul nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-17: gang gis dge 'dun la ras zung gcig po nyos pa'i dge slong des gos kyi gdang la bzhag go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-18: de nas yi dvags mo de mtshan mo 'ongs nas brkus so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-20: chu smad song ste yi dvags mo spyos nas phyir bkug ste byin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-21: de bzhin du lan gsum gyi bar du dge slong de las brkus nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-23: dge slong des kyang de shes nas phyogs bzhi'i dge slong gi dge 'dun gyi phyir stan la klan to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199a-24: de nas de phyin chad ma brkus so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199b-2: ser sna spang ba la brtson par bya'o //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:199b-35: na bza' dang; zhal zas dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:200a-0: mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal @200a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:200a-1: byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:200a-5: mnyan du yod par bsod snyoms byas nas zan zos te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:200a-20: yid du mi 'ong ba myong zhing 'dug pa zhig mthong ngo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:200a-23: khyod kyis sngon sdig pa'i las ci zhig byas nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:200a-26: nyi ma shar ba na sgron ma mi dgos kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:200a-27: bcom ldan 'das la don 'di zhus shig dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:200b-2: de nas tshe dang ldan pa dga' byed bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ngo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:200b-6: de nas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni gsong por gsung ba /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-3: yid du mi 'ong ba myong zhing mchis pa zhig mthong lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-5: lus chen ri bo mthon po 'dra ba la //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-6: mchu dang lkog ma skam zhing shin tu sdug /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-7: rang gi skras ni gdong yog gcer bur mchis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-8: mchu sgo phra khab mig 'dra rab tu rid //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-9: de ltar gcer bu skras yog pa //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-12: ngu zhing kun tu rgyugs par bgyid //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-13: bkres pa dang ni skom pa yis //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-14: dub cing sdug bsngal dag gis nyen //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-15: nyam thag skad kyang 'byin par bgyid //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-16: sdug bsngal tshor ba nyams su myong //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-17: de yis mi yi 'jig rten du //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-18: rab 'jigs sdig pa ci bgyis na //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201a-24: de'i las kyi rnam pa nyan par 'dod dam /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201b-0: bde bar gshegs @201b pa; 'jig rten mkhyen pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201b-4: mi rnams kyi ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'od srung zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201b-15: de nas des sbyin bdag khyim bdag rnams dad pas nges par 'bul ba'ang gcod du bcug /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:201b-17: mi slob pa'i dge slong ma rnams kyi bsngags pa ma yin pa'ang brjod /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:202a-7: dge slong tshul khrims dang ldan pa rnams mthong na mig btsums pas ni dmus long du gyur to //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207a-18: des lha mnyes par byas kyang bu'ang ma byung /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207a-20: de'i blo 'di lta bu zhig skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207a-22: bdag gis chung ma zhig blangs na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207a-23: brgya la bu yod par gyur lta srid dam snyam ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207a-24: des rigs mnyam pa las chung ma blangs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207a-25: de de dang lhan cig tu rtse zhing dga' la dga' mgur spyod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207a-26: de rtse zhing dga' la dga' mgur spyod pa las phyi zhig na bu chags par gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207a-27: de dga' zhing mgu la rab tu dga' nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-1: bdag gi rum g-yas logs na rten cing gnas pa las na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-3: dgyes pa bskyed du gsol zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-6: lag pa g-yas pa ni brkyang nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-7: bdag gis yun ring po nas smon smon pa'i bu'i ngo mthong bar 'ong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-8: bdag gis bu rung bar shog cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-9: mi rung bar ma gyur cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-10: bdag gi bya ba dag byed par shog cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-11: gsos pa'i lan phyir gsol bar shog cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-12: nor skal la spyod par shog cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-13: bdag gi rigs rgyud ring du gnas par shog cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-14: bdag cag 'das te shi ba'i 'og tu'ang bdag cag gi phyir mang yang rung /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-16: sbyin ba dag byin la bsod nams dag byas nas de gnyis gang dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-17: gang du skyes shing 'gro ba der 'di song zhig ces yon bsngo bar shog cig ces dga' ba'i tshig brjod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-18: de nas des bu chags par rig nas bu'i rim gro bya ba'i phyir khang bzang gi steng du nyam rangs su bzhag ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-19: grang ba'i tshe grang ba'i yo byad rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-20: tsha ba'i tshe tsha ba'i yo byad rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-21: sman pas bstan pa'i zas rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-22: ha cang kha ba ma yin pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-23: ha cang skyur ba ma yin pa rnams dang; ha cang lan tshva ba ma yin pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-24: ha cang mdar ba ma yin pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-25: ha cang ro tsha ba ma yin pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:207b-26: ha cang bskal ba ma yin pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-4: bska ba med pa'i zas rnams kyis bsten cing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-6: se mo do lus rnam par klubs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-7: lha'i bu mo dga' ba'i tshal na rnam par rgyu ba bzhin du khri'i steng nas khri'i steng dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-8: khri'u'i steng nas khri'u'i steng du rgyu zhing 'og gi sa gzhi la mi 'bab pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-9: des yid du mi 'ong ba'i sgra skad ci yang mi thos par byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-10: de nas chung ma snga ma des de bkur zhing gces par byed pa mthong nas phrag dog skyes te sems pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-11: gal te 'di las bu btsas par gyur na ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-12: bdag la gnod pa byed par 'gyur gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-13: ci nas de'i thabs shig bya dgos snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-14: 'dod pa la yongs su bsten pa la ni sdig pa'i las mi bya ba'i bag ci yang med de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-15: mi sdug pa'i 'gro ba'i g-yang sar kha bltas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-16: des yid rton du bcug nas gang 'thungs pa tsam gyis nyon mongs ma de'i bu 'phyil bar 'gyur ba de lta bu'i mngal rlug pa'i rtsi byin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-17: de nas chung ma phyi ma des nye du thams cad bsdus nas chung ma snga ma de zhal lce la bkug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-18: khyod kyis bdag yid rton du bcug nas mngal rlug pa'i rtsi byin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-19: des bdag gi bu 'phyil to zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208a-20: de nas chung ma snga ma des nye du rnams kyi nang du mna'ang bor te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-0: gal te bdag gis khyod la mngal rlug pa'i rtsi byin par @208b gyur na bdag yi dvags mor gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-1: bu byung ngo cog za bar shog cig byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-4: tshong dpon gyi chung mar gyur pa gang yin pa de ni yi dvags mo de yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-5: des sngon phrag dog byas pa des na yi dvags mor skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-6: des brdzun byas te mna' bor ba'i las kyi rnam par smin pa des ni nyin mo dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-7: mtshan mo bu lnga lnga btsa' zhing za bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-9: de bas na khyod kyis ngag gi nyes pa spang ba la brtson par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-10: ci nas yi dvags mo de'i nyes pa de lta bu dag 'byung bar mi 'gyur ba de ltar 'dam bu sbyin gyi bu khyod kyis bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-12: tshe dang ldan pa 'dam bu sbyin gyi bu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-17: lto 'phye chen po la sogs pa gzhan dag kyang yi rangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-18: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-19: gang po la sogs pa'i rtogs pa brjod pa brgya pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-21: phyi sa khung zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-22: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-23: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:208b-25: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-2: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-11: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-18: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa yangs pa can na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-19: sbre'u rdzing gi 'gram khang pa brtsegs pa'i gnas na rten cing bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-20: de'i tshe yangs pa can na grong khyer 'obs shig gi nang na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-21: yi dvags zas su skyugs pa za ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-29: rang bzhin gyis sdug bsngal ba lnga brgya gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-31: skyugs pa za zhing bor ba za //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-32: ngar snabs gcin gyis 'tsho ba dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-33: rnag khrag dang ni phyi sa za //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-34: mi bzad rang bzhin sdug cing 'dug /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-35: yangs pa can de na bram ze zhig kyang 'dug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-36: des rigs mnyam pa las chung ma blangs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-37: de de dang lhan cig tu rtse dga' la dga' mgur spyod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209a-38: de rtse zhing dga' la dga' mgur spyod pa las /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-0: chung ma la bu chags nas de'i lus dri nga bar @209b gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-1: de nas bram ze des mtshan mkhan rnams bkug ste dris na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-3: 'di ni lto na khye'u 'dug pa de'i mthu yin no zhes zer ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-4: re zhig na de zla ba brgyad dam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-5: dgu lon pa dang bu byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-6: khye'u mdog ngan cing blta na mi sdug la byad ngan po lus mi gtsang bas bsgos pa dri nga ba zhig btsas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-7: de mchog tu mi sdug mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-8: byams pa'i dbang gis sbrel bas pha ma gnyis kyis gsos so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-9: de mi gtsang ba'i gnas rnams 'ba' zhig tu dga' la phyag dar gyi phung po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-10: phyis khung du skra 'bal zhing khar mi gtsang ba 'dzud nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-11: de'i ming phyis khung zhes bya bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-12: re zhig na de phan tshun du 'khyam pa las 'od srung rdzogs byed kyis mthong nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-14: 'di de lta bu'i gnas rnams su dga' ba las na 'di ni gor ma chags par grub pa'i skyes bu zhig yin gyi bdag gis 'dir rab tu dbyung ngo snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-15: des de rab tu phyung nas gcer bur 'khyam zhing 'dug la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-16: legs pa byed pa la'ang gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-17: de nas de 'khyam zhing song ba las yangs pa can gyi 'obs kyi nang na yi dvags lnga brgya 'khod pa rnams mthong nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-18: de sngon gyi las kyi rnam par smin pa dang 'brel pas grong khyer gyi 'obs de'i nang du song nas de dag dang lhan cig 'dus shing phrad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-19: dga' bar gyur nas grogs por gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:209b-20: phyis re zhig na khye'u phyis khung don zhig la brel te yangs pa can du song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-1: 'das kyang grong khyer gyi 'obs der byon nas yi dvags de dag gis sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das sku skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis legs par brgyan pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-4: nyi ma stong pas lhag pa'i 'od mnga' ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-5: rin po che'i ri bo 'gro ba lta bu kun nas bzang pa mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-6: mthong ma thag tu bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag btsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-7: bcom ldan 'das bdag cag phongs lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-10: yi dvags rnams kyis smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-12: bdag cag ni skom lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-13: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis phyag sor lnga las yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i chu'i rgyun lnga phab ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-14: des yi dvags lnga brgya po de dag tshim par mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-15: de nas de dag bcom ldan 'das la sems dga' bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-16: shi nas sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha yul bzang por skyes so; ;lha'i bu'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-17: lha'i bu mo skyes nas ring po ma lon pa ni chos nyid kyis sems rnam pa gsum skye bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-20: las gang gis ksyes snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-21: de nas yi dvags las shi 'phos pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-22: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha yul bzang por skyes pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210a-23: bcom ldan 'das la sems dga' bar gyur par de dag gis mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-0: de nas @210b sngon yi dvags su gyur pa'i lha'i bu de dag 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-2: gzod bcom ldan 'das la blta ba'i phyir /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-3: 'gro ba ni bdag cag gi cha ma yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-4: bdag cag zhag ma lon par bcom ldan 'das la blta ba'i phyir 'dong ngo snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-5: de nas sngon yi dvags su gyur pa'i lha'i bu rna cha gdub kor dag cing 'gul pa thogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-8: nor bu sna tshogs kyis spras pa'i cod pan can /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-10: ta ma la'i lo ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-11: spri ka la sogs pas byugs pa de rnams kyi de nyid kyi mtshan mo lha'i me tog autpa la dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-15: man d'a ra rnams kyis thu ba bkang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-16: khang pa brtsegs pa'i gnas thams cad 'od chen pos snang bar byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-17: bcom ldan 'das la me tog gis gtor te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-18: chos mnyan pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'khod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-19: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis sngon yi dvags su gyur pa'i lha'i bu rnams kyi bsam pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-22: rang bzhin thugs su chud nas 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi rtogs par 'gyur ba de lta bu'i chos bstan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-23: de thos nas lha'i bu lnga brgyas 'jig tshogs la lta ba'i ri'i rtse mo mthon po nyi shu ye shes rdo rjes bcom nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-24: rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu thob ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:210b-25: de dag gis bden pa mthong nas tshong pa khe spogs phyin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-1: pa 'bru rgyal bar gyur pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-2: dpa' bo g-yul las rgyal ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-3: nad pa nad thams cad las thar ba bzhin du 'byor ba gang gis bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du lhags pa'i 'byor ba de nyid kyis bcom ldan 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas nas rang gi gnas su dong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-4: de nas khye'u phyi sa khung grong khyer gyi 'obs su 'ongs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-5: yi dvags de dag ma mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-6: de nas tshol ba la zhugs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-7: de de dag yongs su tshol bas skyo bar 'gyur la de dag ni ma rnyed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-8: de'i skabs su sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis ni mi mkhyen pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-11: thugs su mi chud pa zhig ci yang med la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-12: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thugs rje chen po dang ldan la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-13: 'jig rten la phan 'dogs pa la zhugs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-14: srung ba gcig pa dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-20: rig pa gsum snang bar mdzad pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-21: bslab pa gsum legs par bslabs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-22: 'dul ba'i gzhi gsum la mkhas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-23: chu bo bzhi las brgal ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-24: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi'i zhabs kyi mthil shin tu brtan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-25: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi la yun ring po nas 'dris par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211a-27: khyu mchog gi yang dag pa'i seng ge'i sgra chen po sgrogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-0: yan @211b lag lnga rnams par spangs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-1: 'gro ba lnga las yang dag par 'das pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-2: yan lag drug dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-3: pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-4: rtag tu gnas par bya ba drug la gnas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-5: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun gyi me tog gis phyug pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-6: lam yan lag brgyad pa ston pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-7: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu la mkhas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-8: stobs bcu'i stobs dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-9: phyogs bcur grags pas kun tu rgyas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-10: brgya phrag bcu pa la dbang byed pa pas ches khyad par du 'phags pa rnams ni chos nyid kyis nyin dus gsum /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-11: mtshan dus gsum du sangs rgyas kyi spyan gyis 'jig rten la gzigs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-16: su ni gnod pa dang ldan /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-20: su ni ngan song du gzhol /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-22: su ni ngan song du bab /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-23: su ni ngas ngan song las phyung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-27: su ni 'dod pa'i 'dam du bying ba las lag nas drang bar bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-28: su ni 'phags pa'i nor bdun med pa las 'phags pa'i nor bdun gyi dbang phyug la dbang byed du gzhug par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-29: su ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams ma bskyed pas bskyed par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:211b-30: su ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams bskyed zin pa las yongs su smin par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-0: su ni yongs su smin zin pa las rnam par grol bar bya snyam du ye shes @212a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-3: rgya mtsho chu srin rnams kyi gnas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-4: dus rlabs yol bar 'gyur yang srid //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-6: sangs rgyas dus las yol ba med //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-7: de nas bcom ldan 'das rigs kyi bu phyi sa khung la phan gdags pa'i phyir snga dro sham thabs dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-13: bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'greng ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-14: de nas des sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das sku skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis legs par brgyan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-15: dbe byad bzang po brgyad cus mdzes par byas ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-17: nyi ma stong bas lhag pa'i 'od mnga' ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-18: rin po che'i ri bo 'gro ba lta bu kun nas bzang ba mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-19: mthong nas kyang de'i mod la des bcom ldan 'das la sems dga' bar byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212a-21: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag btsal te thal mo sbyar nas gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212b-0: gal te sems can bdag cag lta bu'ang legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba 'di la rab tu @212b 'byung ba mchis te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:212b-20: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis de la yid la byed pa'i lung phog ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:213a-20: de nas dge slong dag the tshom skyes te the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:213a-22: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:213b-12: lus can dag gis las rnams ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:213b-13: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:213b-27: bla na med pa lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:213b-29: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'khor ba 'jig ces bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:223b-0: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag @223b btsal te chos mnyan pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'dug go /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:225a-0: @225a *// bcom ldan 'das kyang dge slong gi tshogs kyi zham ring byas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:225b-0: dge ba'i rtsa ba 'bar ba de mthong @225b ngo; ;mthong nas kyang de la tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
