K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-0: dge slong sde snod gsum pa zhig 'khor lnga brgya dang @249b gtan la 'bebs pa'i nang na 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-1: de'i nang na slob pa dang mi slob pa'i dge slong dag kyang yod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-2: de dag sde snod gsum pa la 'dri bar byed la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-3: des ni lan ma thebs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-4: de khros nas ngag gi las rtsub po phyung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-5: nags kyi ma he dang 'dra ba 'di dag ci shes zhes byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-6: de'i slob ma rnams kyis kyang ma he rdzi dang 'dra ba 'di dag ci shes zhes smras so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-10: dge slong sde snod gsum pa gang yin pa de nyid ma he 'di yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-11: slob ma de dag ni ma he rdzi 'di dag yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-12: las des na che rabs lnga brgyar ma her skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-13: slob ma rnams kyang ma he rdzi lnga brgyar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-14: nga la sems dga' bar gyur pa des ni lhar skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-15: dge slong gi dngos po thob ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-16: tshul khrims bsrungs pas ni bden pa mthong ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-17: dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-19: de bas na ngag gi nyes pa spangs pa'i phyir 'bad par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-21: ma he rdzi rnams kyi nyes pa de lta bu dag 'byung bar mi 'gyur ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-22: lha'i bu de'i yon tan gyi tshogs de lta bu thob par 'gyur bar dge slong khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-23: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-24: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:249b-25: bsnyen gnas zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-1: bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-2: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-4: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-13: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-23: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-30: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-31: de'i tshe sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha'i nang na lha'i bu bsnyen gnas zhes bya ba zhig yod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-32: de chos nyan pa'i phyir rtag tu bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du 'gro'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-33: de nas phyis re zhig na lha'i bu bsnyen gnas g-yog 'khor lnga brgya dang bcas pa bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250a-34: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la mgo bos phyag btsal te chos nyan pa'i phyir phyogs gcig tu 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-0: de nas bcom @250b ldan 'das kyis lha'i bu bsnyen gnas kyi bsam pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-3: rang bzhin thugs su chud nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-4: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi rtogs par 'gyur ba de lta bu'i chos bstan te; de thos nas lha'i bu bsnyen gnas kyi 'jig tshogs la lta ba'i ri'i rtse mo mthon po nyi shu ye shes rdo rjes bcom nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-5: rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu thob ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-6: des bden pa mthong nas dga' ba'i tshig lan gsum du brjod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-7: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag gi khrag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-8: mchil ma'i rgya mtsho bskams pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-9: rus pa'i la bsgral ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-10: ngan song gi sgo rnams bcad pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-12: thar pa'i sgo rnams phye ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-14: mi rnams kyi nang du bzhag pa 'di lta bu ni bdag la phas kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-17: lha rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-19: gnyen gyi tshogs rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-20: sngon gyi mtshun rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-22: bram ze rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-24: nyes pa mang por ldan pa'i ngan song lam //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-25: shin tu mi bzad khyod kyi mthu yis bcad //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-26: bsod nams rab ldan mtho ris 'gro ba phye //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-27: mya ngan 'das pa'i lam yang bdag gis thob //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-28: bdag gis de ring nyes pa spangs pa'i mig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-29: shin tu rnam dag khyod la brten nas thob //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-30: bdag ni sdug bsngal rgya mtsho pha rol brgal //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:250b-31: 'phags pa dgyes pa'i zhi ba'i go 'phang thob //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-1: dbang po mi dang lhas mchod pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-2: skye dang rga dang 'chi ba'i nad spangs pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-3: srid pa stong du mthong bar dka' ba yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-4: thub pa khyod ni deng mthong 'bras bu yod //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-5: de nas do shal 'phyang ba dga' gyur te //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-6: btud cing zhabs gnyis la ni phyag btsal nas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-7: dgra thub la ni bskor ba byas nas kyang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-8: lha yi 'jig rten kha bltas lha yul song //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-9: de nas lha'i bu bsnyen gnas tshong pa khe spogs phyin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-10: zhing pa 'bru rgyal bar gyur pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-11: dpa' po g-yul las rgyal ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-12: nad pa nad thams cad las thar ba bzhin du 'byor ba gang gis bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du 'ongs pa'i 'byor ba de nyid kyis rang gi gnas su song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-13: de'i tshe dge slong dag srod dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-14: tho rangs mi nyal bar brtson pa lhur byed pa la gnas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-15: de dag gis bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du snang ba chen po byung ba mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-16: mthong nas kyang the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-17: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-19: mdang sum mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-20: lha'i dbang po brgya byin nam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-21: 'jig rten skyong ba bzhi bcom ldan 'das la blta ba'i slad du mchis lags sam; bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-23: mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251a-24: lha'i dbang po brgya byin nam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-0: 'jig rten skyong ba bzhi nga la blta ba'i phyir 'ongs pa ma @251b yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-1: lha'i bu bsnyen gnas g-yog 'khor lnga brgya dang bcas pa nga la blta ba'i phyir 'ongs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-2: ngas de la chos bstan nas bden pa mthong bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-3: rang gi gnas su song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-6: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-8: lha'i bu bsnyen gnas ga las byung lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-9: ming ni ci las btags lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-10: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-18: 'o na legs par rab tu nyon la yid la zungs shig ngas bshad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-20: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-21: bskal pa bzang po 'di nyid la skye dgu'i tshe lo nyi khri thub pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-24: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-29: skyes bu 'dul bya'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-33: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'od srung zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-34: de grong khyer w'a ra n'a si na drang srong smra ba ri dvags kyi nags na rten cing bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-35: phyis re zhig na rgyal po kri kr'i bcom ldan 'das la blta ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-36: bsnyen bkur bya ba'i phyir song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-37: de nas re zhig na bram ze gnyis drang srong smra bar don zhig la song ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:251b-38: de gnyis kyis rgyal po de rgyal po'i 'byor ba chen po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-1: mthu stobs chen po dang ldan pa mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-2: de nas de gnyis rgyal srid la 'dod pa skyes nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-3: de gnyis kyis dge bsnyen zhig la dris pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-4: kye sangs rgyas kyi dge bsnyen /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-7: ci 'dod pa de dag thams cad 'grub par 'gyur zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-9: gang gis bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa yongs su dag par bsrungs pa de'i ni ci bsams pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-10: ci 'dod pa de dag thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-11: de nas bram ze de gnyis kyis khyim bdag chu stod las bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa blangs te bsrungs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-12: de na gcig gis ni yongs su dag par bsrungs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-13: de nas shi nas rgyal po kri kri'i bur skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-14: de'i ming legs skyes zhes btags nas pha shi ba'i 'og tu de rgyal por bcug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-15: gcig shos kyis ni bsnyen gnas nyams par byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-16: de ni shi nas klu'i nang du skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-17: de'i steng du nyin gcig bzhin du lan bdun bdun bye tshan bab ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-18: des rus pa 'ba' zhig lus par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-19: de nas de 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-21: 'di las gang gis 'bras bu'i rnam par smin pa yin na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252a-22: des bdag gi 'di lta bu'i sdug bsngal myong zhing 'dug snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-0: de nas des bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa bdag gis blangs pa las bslab pa lhod par byas pa des 'di lta @252b bu'i sdug bsngal bdag gis nyams su myong la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-2: bsrungs pa des ni rgyal srid thob par gyur to snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-3: yang de 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-4: de'ang bdag gis bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad dang ldan par bsrung bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-5: 'o na tang bdag klu'i skye gnas las thar bar 'gyur yang srid do snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-6: de nas bram ze'i cha lugs su bdag nyid sprul nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-7: rgyal po'i thad du 'ongs te phyin nas rgyal po la rgyal bar gyur cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-8: sku tshe ring bar shog cig ces bstod nas smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-10: bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa bdag la 'tshal gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-11: lha; bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa btsal du gsol /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-12: gal te ma btsal na gdon mi 'tshal bar lha'i dbu tshal ba bdun du 'gas par 'gyur ro zhes byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-13: de nyid du mi snang bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-14: de nas rgyal po 'jigs shing skrag ste mi dga' las kyi bung zhes byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-15: gser 'bum yod pa'i snod rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-16: bdag gi yul thams cad du dril bsgrags nas; su nga la bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa ston pa de la gser 'bum 'di sbyin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-17: bkur sti chen pos kyang bsnyen bkur bya'o zhes bsgo'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-18: de nas re zhig na shing mkhan gyi bu mo bud med rgan mo zhig 'dug pa des rgyal po la ka ba zhig bstan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:252b-19: sngon bdag gi pha rtag tu ka ba 'di la spos dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-0: me tog gis mchod pa bgyid na 'di phyung ste gzigs @253a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-2: de nas rgyal pos zham ring ba rnams la ka ba 'di phyungs shig ces bsgo'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-3: de nas rgyal po'i zham ring rnams kyis ka ba de phyung ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-4: de'i 'og nas bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-5: dge bsnyen gyi bslab pa'i gzhi lnga dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-6: byang chub kyi phyogs dang mthun pa'i chos sum cu rtsa bdun gser gyi glegs bam la bris pa zhig rnyed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-7: de nas rgyal pos klu de la bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa zhig bris te byin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-8: drang srong smra ba na gnas pa'i drang srong khri nyis stong gis kyang byang chub kyi phyogs dang mthun pa'i chos sum cu rtsa bdun mngon sum du byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-9: klu des kyang bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa bsrungs nas thang la byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-10: lus bor nas de kha 'tshos te 'dug go ;de nas shi ste g-yog 'khor lnga brgya dang bcas te sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha yul bzang por skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-12: bsnyen gnas ni de nas byung ste ming yang de las btags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-14: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-15: ngang pa zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-16: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-17: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253a-19: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253b-6: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253b-16: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253b-23: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253b-24: de'i tshe mnyan du yod pa na ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal rgyal po byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253b-30: mi mang pos gang ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253b-41: ma he dang ldan par 'dug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253b-42: gnod pa med cing tsher ma dkrugs la bu gcig pa la bya ba bzhin du rgyal srid bskyangs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:253b-43: phyis re zhig na ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal bcom ldan 'das la blta ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-0: bsnyen bkur bya ba'i phyir rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal du song @254a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-2: panytsa la'i rgyal pos ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal la ngang pa lnga brgya skyes su bskur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-3: gang gi tshe rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal du song ba de'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-4: ngang pa lnga brgya po de dag phul lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-5: de nas rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis ngang pa de dag la mi 'jigs pa byin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-6: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal de nyid du btang nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-7: gang gi tshe bcom ldan 'das nyan thos chen po'i 'khor dang bcas pa bshos gsol zhing bzhugs pa de'i tshe ngang pa de dag bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du 'gro la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-8: bcom ldan 'das dang nyan thos chen po de dag gis kyang de rnams khyos ma byin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-9: de dag gis zos nas tshim zhing mgu la dbang po rtas te 'khod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-10: gang gi tshe bcom ldan 'das nang du yang dag 'jog las bzhengs nas 'khor bzhi po de dag la chos ston pa de'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-11: ngang pa de dag bcom ldan 'das kyi thang du dong ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-13: de nas de dag tshe thung ste shi nas sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha yul bzang por skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-14: lha'i bu'am lha'i bu mo skyes nas ring po ma lon pa ni chos nyid kyis sems rnam pa gsum skye bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-17: las gang gis skyes snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-18: de nas ngang pa las shi 'phos pa dang sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha yul bzang por skyes pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254a-19: bcom ldan 'das la sems dga' bar gyur pa de dag gis mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-0: de nas @254b sngon ngang par gyur pa'i lha'i bu rnams 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-1: bdag cag zhag lon nas gzod bcom ldan 'das la blta ba'i phyir 'gro ba ni bdag cag gi cha ma yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-2: bdag cag zhag ma lon par bcom ldan 'das la blta ba'i phyir 'gro'o snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-3: de nas sngon ngang par gyur pa'i lha'i bu rna cha gdub ko ra dag cing 'gul ba thogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-6: nor bu rin po che sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa'i cod pan can /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-8: ta ma la'i lo ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-9: spri ka la sogs pas byugs pa de dag gis de nyid kyi mtshan mo lha'i me tog autpa la dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-13: man d'a ra rnams kyi thu ba bkang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-14: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal thams cad 'od chen pos snang bar byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-15: bcom ldan 'das la me tog gis gtor te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-16: chos nyan pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar 'khod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-17: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis sngon ngang par gyur pa'i lha'i bu rnams kyi bsam pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-20: rang bzhin thugs su chud nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-21: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi rtogs par 'gyur ba de lta bu'i chos bstan te; de thos nas sngon ngang par gyur pa'i lha'i bu rnams kyis 'jig tshogs la lta ba'i ri'i rtse mo mthon po nyi shu ye shes rdo rjes bcom nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:254b-22: rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu thob ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-1: dag gis bden pa mthong nas dga' ba'i tshig lan gsum brjod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-2: btsun pa bcom ldan 'das kyis bdag cag gi khrag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-3: mchi ma'i rgya mtsho bskams pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-4: rus pa'i la bsgral ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-5: ngan song gi sgo bcad pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-7: thar pa'i sgo rnams phye ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-9: mi rnams kyi nang du bzhag pa 'di lta bu ni bdag cag la phas kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-12: lha rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-14: gnyen gyi tshogs kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-15: sngon gyi mtshun rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-17: bram ze rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-19: nyes pa mang por ldan pa'i ngan song lam //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-20: shin tu mi bzad khyod kyi mthu yis bcad //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-21: bsod nams rab ldan mtho ris 'gro ba phye //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-22: mya ngan 'das lam bdag cag rnams kyis thob //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-23: bdag cag de ring nyes pa spangs pa'i mig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-24: shin tu rnam dag khyod la brten nas thob //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-25: bdag cag sdug bsngal rgya mtsho'i pha rol brgal //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-26: 'phags pa dgyes pa'i zhi ba'i go 'phang thob //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-27: mi mchog dbang po mi dang lhas mchod pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-28: skye dang rga dang 'chi ba'i nad spangs pa //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-29: srid pa stong du mthong bar dka' ba yi //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-30: thub pa khyod ni deng mthong 'bras bu yod //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-31: de nas do shal 'phyang rnams dga' gyur te //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255a-32: btud cing zhabs gnyis la ni phyag btsal nas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-0: @255b dgra thub la ni bskor ba byas nas kyang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-1: lha yi 'jig rten kha bltas lha yul song //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-2: de nas sngon ngang par gyur pa'i lha'i bu rnams tshong pa khe spogs phyin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-3: zhing pa 'bru rgyal bar gyur pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-4: dpa' bo g-yul las rgyal ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-5: nad pa nad thams cad las thar ba bzhin du 'byor pa gang gis bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du lhags pa'i 'byor pa de nyid kyis rang gi gnas su dong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-6: de'i tshe dge slong srod dang tho rangs mi nyal bar brtson pa lhur byed pa la gnas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-7: de dag gis bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du snang ba chen po byung ba mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-8: mthong nas kyang the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-9: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-11: mdang sum mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-12: lha'i dbang po brgya byin nam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-13: 'jig rten skyong ba bzhi bcom ldan 'das la blta ba'i slad du mchis lags sam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-16: mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-17: lha'i dbang po brgya byin nam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-18: 'jig rten skyong ba bzhi nga la blta ba'i phyir 'ongs pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-20: ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis ngang pa lnga brgya 'dir btang ba khyod kyis mthong ngam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-24: de dag nga la sems dga' bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:255b-25: shi nas sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha yul bzang por skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-1: nga'i thad du lhags nas de dag la ngas chos bstan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-2: bden pa mthong bar gyur nas rang gi gnas su dong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-3: de nas dge slong dag the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-4: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-6: sngon ngang par gyur pa'i lha'i bu rnams kyis las gang dag bgyis na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-8: las gang dag bgyis na des lha'i nang du skyes te bden pa mthong lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-9: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-11: 'di dag nyid kyis sngon tshe rabs gzhan dag tu tshogs rnyed cing rkyen grub pa dang ldan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-13: gdon mi za bar 'ong ba'i las de dag byas shing bsags pas na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-14: sngon ngang par gyur pa'i lha'i bu rnams kyis las byas shing bsags pa de dag gzhan su zhig gis nyams su myong bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-16: las byas shing bsags pa rnams ni phyi rol gyi sa'i khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-20: las dge ba dang mi dge ba byas shing bsags pa rnams ni zin pa'i phung po dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-23: lus can dag gi las rnams ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-24: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256a-25: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-2: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na bskal pa bzang po 'di nyid la skye dgu'i tshe lo nyi khri thub pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-5: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-10: skyes bu 'dul bya'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-14: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'od srung zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-15: de grong khyer w'a ra n'a si na drang srong smra ba ri dvags kyi nags na rten cing bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-16: de'i tshe 'di dag rab tu byung ba las bslab pa la lhod bar byas pa des ni ngang par skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-17: nga la sems dga' bar byas pa des ni lhar skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-18: bslab pa lhag pa rnams bsrungs pa des ni bden pa mthong bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-20: de ltar na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams ni rnam par smin pa'ang gcig tu nges par gnag par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-21: las gcig tu nges par dkar ba ni rnam par smin pa'ang gcig tu nges par dkar bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-22: las 'dren ma rnams ni rnam par smin pa'ang 'dren mar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-24: de bas na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-26: las gcig tu nges par dkar ba rnams 'ba' zhig la gtad par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:256b-28: khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-0: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces @257a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-2: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-3: gang po la sogs pa'i rtogs pa brjod pa brgya pa las /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-4: sdom gyi tshigs su bcad pa drug pa rdzogs so ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-6: gser 'od dang ni dri zhim dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-7: byad bzang stobs ldan sdug gu dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-8: padma mig dang rnga sgra dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-9: bu dang nyi ma gyad pa dang //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-12: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-14: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-23: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis [?] bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-33: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257a-40: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa ser skya'i gnas na shing n+ya gro dha'i kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-0: de'i tshe ser skya'i gnas na sh'akya phyug cing nor @257b mang la longs spyod che ba yongs su 'dzin pa yangs shing rgya che ba rnam thos kyi bu'i nor dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-1: rnam thos kyi bu'i nor dang 'gran pa zhig gnas pa des /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-2: rigs mnyam pa las chung ma blangs nas; de de dang lhan cig tu rtse zhing dga' la dga' mgur spyod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-3: de rtse zhing dga' la dga' mgur spyod pa las chung ma la bu chags nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-5: dgu lon pa dang bu byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-6: khye'u gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa mi'i kha dog las ni 'das /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-12: de na de btsas pa'i btsas ston byas nas khye'u 'di'i ming ji skad gdags zhes ming 'dogs par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-14: 'di btsas pa na grong khyer ser skya'i gnas thams cad gser gyi 'od kyis snang bar byas pas na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-15: de'i phyir khye'u 'di'i ming gser 'od ces gdags so zhes zer ro; ;de nas khye'u gser 'od bang na 'tsho ba'i ma ma gnyis dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:257b-18: rtse ba'i ma ma gnyis te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258a-15: grong khyer gyi phyi rol na rtse zhing 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258a-16: sh'akya mang po dag gcig kyang shing n+ya gro dha'i kun dga' ra bar dong ngo //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258a-20: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la blta ba'i phyir shing n+ya gro dha'i kun dga' ra bar 'gro'o //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258a-25: bdag kyang sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das blta ba'i phyir 'gro gor ma chags snyam nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258a-26: de'ang shing n+ya gro dha'i kun dga' ra bar song ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258a-27: khye'u gser 'od kyis sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das sku skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis legs par brgyan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258b-0: @258b dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus mdzes par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258b-2: nyi ma stong bas lhag pa'i 'od mnga' ba /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258b-17: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis phyag gser gyi kha dog can glang po che'i sna ltar 'dug pa brkyang nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:258b-21: de skad ces bka' stsal pa'i mod la /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:259a-2: lag na ni lhung bzed dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:259a-3: chu snod thogs par gyur te //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-6: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi bstan pa 'di la gdul bar bya ba mang po dag des 'dren par 'gyur bar thugs su chud nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-9: song la 'khor rnams kyang ltos shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-10: de nas bu mo 'od bzang ma rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal nas byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-11: mang po 'dus pa'i nang du song ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-12: der so so nas bsams pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-13: 'di mthus dbrog par bya'o snyam ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-14: de dag gis bzung bar byas so; ;de nas bu mo 'od bzang ma de dag gis bsnyegs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-15: ngang pa'i rgyal po 'dab ma brkyang ba bzhin du nam mkha' la mngon par 'phags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-16: cho 'phrul rnam pa sna tshogs bstan to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-17: so so'i skye bo rnams ni rdzu 'phrul gyis myur du dad par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294a-18: de nas de dag gis lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-0: mi rnams dad par byed pa'i cho 'phrul de mthong @294b ngo; ;mthong nas kyang spu zing zhes byas nas sdong po rtsa ba nas bcad pa bzhin du rkang pa la phyag btsal nas gsol ba btab pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-5: khyod kyis chos 'di lta bu dag mngon sum du byas pa las na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-6: khyod 'dod pa spyod pa 'di ni mi srid do zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-7: de nas bu mo 'od bzang ma nam mkha' las babs nas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-8: skye bo phal po che'i gung la 'dug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-9: gang thos pas srog chags 'bum phrag du mas bden pa mthong bar 'gyur ba de lta bu'i chos bstan to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-10: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi skye dgu'i bdag mo chen mo la gtad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-11: des de rab tu phyung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-12: bsnyen par rdzogs par byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-13: de nas des brtson pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-15: 'bad pas phol mig lnga pa'i 'khor lo 'di nyid g-yo zhing mi brtan par rig nas 'du byed kyi rnam pa thams cad snyil ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-18: rnam par 'jig pa'i chos can yin par rtsad chod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-19: nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs nas dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-20: dgra bcom pa khams gsum pa'i 'dod chags dang bral bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-22: bong bar mnyam pa; nam mkha' dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-23: lag mthil du 'dra ba'i sems dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-24: tsandan spangs pa lta bur bsil bar gyur pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:294b-25: rig pas sgo nga'i sbubs bcom pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-2: so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-5: bkur sti la mi lta ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-7: nye dbang dang bcas pa'i lha rnams kyis mchod cing rjed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-8: gus par smra ba'i gnas su gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-9: de nas dge slong dag the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-10: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-12: 'od bzang mas las gang dag bgyis na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-13: des gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-14: mgul pa nas kyang nor bu rin po che byung la rab tu byung nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-15: dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du bgyis lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-16: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-18: 'od bzang ma nyid kyis sngon tshe rabs gzhan dag tu tshogs rnyed cing rkyen grub pa dang ldan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-19: dba' rgal bzhin du 'byung la gdon mi za bar 'ong ba'i las de dag byas shing bsags pas na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-20: 'od bzang ma nyid kyis las byas shing bsags pa de dag gzhan su zhig gis nyams su myong bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-22: las byas shing bsags pa rnams ni phyi rol gyi sa'i khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295a-25: rlung gi khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-0: @295b mi dge ba byas shing bsags pa rnams ni zin pa'i phung po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-2: skye mched rnams 'ba' zhig la rnam par smin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-3: lus can dag gi las rnams ni; ;bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-4: tshogs shing dus la bab ba na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-7: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-8: bskal pa dgu bcu rtsa gcig pa la de bzhin gshegs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-10: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rig pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-14: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-18: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnam par gzigs zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-19: de rgyal po'i pho brang gnyen ldan na rten cing bzhugs pa las re zhig na yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs sangs rgyas kyi 'phrin las thams cad mdzad nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-20: shing zad pa'i me bzhin du phung po'i lhag ma med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su yongs su mya ngan las 'das so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-21: de nas rgyal po gnyan yod kyis bcom ldan 'das de'i sku gdung la sku gdung gi mchod pa byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:295b-22: rin po che sna bzhi las byas pa'i mchod rten kho ra khor yug tu dpag tshad gcig yod la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-2: de nas re zhig na rgyal po gnyen yod kyi btsun mo dam pa rgas nas rgyan rnam pa sna tshogs lus las bkrol te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-3: mchod rten de la phul lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-4: de nas zhabs la phyag btsal te smon lam btab pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-7: sbyin par bya ba'i chos yongs su gtong ba 'dis na; bdag gis kyang dgra bcom pa nyid thob par gyur cig ces byas so; ;bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-10: de'i tshe de'i dus na rgyal po gnyen yod kyi btsun mo dam par gyur pa gang yin pa de ni 'od bzang ma 'di yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-11: des bcom ldan 'das rnam par gzigs kyi mchod rten la rnam pa sna tshogs btags pa de na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-12: gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-14: nying lag thams cad dang ldan par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-15: smon lam btab pa des ni da ltar dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-17: de ltar na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams ni rnam par smin pa'ang gcig tu nges par gnag par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296a-18: las gcig tu nges par dkar ba rnams ni rnam par smin pa'ang gcig tu nges par dkar bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-0: las 'dren ma rnams ni rnam par smin pa'ang @296b 'dren mar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-2: de lta bas na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-4: las gcig tu nges par dkar ba rnams 'ba' zhig la gtad par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-5: dge slong khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-7: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-8: rab sdug ma zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-9: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang; blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-11: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-15: klu rnams dang; gnod sbyin rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-19: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:296b-29: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shas pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-1: pa; nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so; ;de'i tshe khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi chung ma la bu chags nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-3: dgu lon pa na bu byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-4: bu mo gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-6: nying lag thams cad dang ldan pa mnyam du yod pa na gnas pa'i skye bo'i tshogs rnams kyi snying du rab tu sdug ma zhig btsas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-7: de nas de btsas pa'i btsas ston byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-8: bu mo 'di'i ming ji skad gdags zhes ming 'dogs par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-10: bu mo 'di skye bo thams cad kyi snying du sdug pas na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-11: de'i phyir bu mo 'di'i ming rab sdug ma zhes gdags so zhes zer ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-13: btsas ma thag tu tshigs su bcad pas smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-14: sbyin pa byin pa mang nyung ci yang rung //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-15: zhing gi khyad par bzhi las 'phel bar 'gyur //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-16: de'i phyir mkhas pas bsgrims te 'jig rten du //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-17: dad pas lha mi'i dbang phyug sangs rgyas sbyin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-18: de nas de'i pha ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-20: khyim de na gnas pa rnams kyis tshig brjod pa de thos nas skrag cing sdangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297a-22: skyi bung zhes byed nas smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-0: bu mo 'di ni sha za mo zhig @297b go ;des smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-2: bdag ni sha za mo'ang ma lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-4: bdag ni bu mo lags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-5: sbyin pa dag sbyin par 'tshal lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-6: de nas de'i mas khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin la bu mo des 'di skad mchi'o zhes bsnyad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-7: de nas khyim bdag de dga' zhing mgu la rab tu dga' nas bcom ldan 'das dge slong gi dge 'dun dang bcas pa khyim gyi nang du bshos gsol te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-8: de'i phyir sbyin pa'i rabs 'don du bcug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-9: de nas gang gi tshe bu mo de mthar gyis lo bdun lon pa de'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyi bstan pa la rab tu byung nas de dge slong ma thams cad la sdug pa dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-18: de nas der bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-20: khyod song la rab sdug ma la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-22: 'khor bzhi po rnams la khyod kyis zla ba gsum gyi bar du gos dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:297b-27: sman zong rnams phul cig ces gyis shig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-0: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo rab sdug ma'i thad du @298a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal nas khyod kyis 'khor bzhi po rnams la zla ba gsum gyi bar du gos dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-6: sman zong rnams phul cig ces bka' stsal to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-7: de nas rab tu sdug mas thal mo sbyar te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-8: bcom ldan 'das kyi bka' spyi bos mnos nas bka' bzhin 'tshal zhes smras so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-9: de nas rab sdug ma spyod yul gyi grong blta ba'i phyir mnyan du yod par chas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-10: de nas re zhig na khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyis gtam de thos nas shin tu rings par rab sdug ma'i mdun du song ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-15: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-17: mgon med zas sbyin gyis smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-18: khyod kyi de dag thams cad bdag gis sbyar gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-19: khyod kyis bya ma dgos so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-22: yab bden pa mthong ba lags so /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-23: sa'i 'og thog thag tu sbas pa'i gter rnams kyang mngon du gzigs na sbyar ba 'di la ngo mtshar che ba ci mchis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-24: 'on kyang bdag ni skye bo dbul po la phan gdags pa'i slad du zhal ta bgyid do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298a-25: de bzhin du dge bsnyen lnga brgya dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-1: rgyal rigs kyi bu mo dbyar tshul ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-2: btsun mo 'khor gyi bla brang srong sbyin dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-4: ri dvags 'dzin gyi ma sa ga dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-5: rgyal po gsal rgyal rnams kyis kyang skabs phye ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-6: khyod kyis bya mi dgos so zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-7: de nas nags khung du song nas der mi yin pa mi'i cha lugs can dag gis kyang skabs phye'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-8: de ltar skabs phye nas kyang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-9: de nas bcom ldan 'das nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa zla ba gsum gyi bar du na bza' dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-14: sman zong rnams kyis bsnyen bkur byas so //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-18: 'du byed kyi rnam pa thams cad snyil ba dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:298b-23: dgra bcom pa khams gsum pa'i 'dod chags dang bral bar gyur nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:299a-0: tsandan spangs ba lta bur bsil @299a *//

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:299a-20: bcom ldan 'das nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa bzhugs par gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:299a-21: de nas lhung bzed lag pa g-yon pa la bzhag ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:299a-23: gal te bsod nams dag gi rnam par smin pa yod ce na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:299a-24: bdag gi lhung bzed bza' ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:299a-25: bca' ba la sogs pa rnam pa sna tshogs kyis gang bar gyur cig ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:299b-0: de nas lhas lha'i bdud @299b rtsis bkang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:299b-1: de nas rab sdug gis gral rims bzhin dge slong gi dge 'dun thams cad kyi lhung bzed rnams zhal zas kyis bkang nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:299b-2: der bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335a-18: 'di'i khyim du song la chung ma blta'o snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335a-19: de nas de dag gis chang gar po sna mi mthun pas gtu lum par bas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-0: lde mig rnams khyer te khyim du song nas sgo rnams phye ste bu mo de mthong @335b ngo; ;mthong nas kyang ya mtshan du gyur te bsams pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-1: gang gas 'di bdag cag la mi bstan ni yus so snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-2: de nas de dag phyir log ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-3: gang ga chang gi dbang gis gnyid log cing 'dug pa las bslang nas smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-5: khyod kyi chung ma de ltar sdug pa ni khyod kyis rnyed pa legs par rnyed do zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-6: de nas gang ga lhag par yang mi dga' bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-7: chad pa'ang bdag gis gcal la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-8: bdag la gtam ngan par yang gyur to snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-9: de nas mi dga' bzhin du bdag gi khyim du 'ongs nas sgo phye ste chung ma la bltas na nags tshal me tog rgyas pa'i nang na nags kyi lha mo 'dug pa bzhin du shin tu mdzes pa mthong nas dris pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-11: ci zhig byas na 'di lta bu'i gzugs khyad par can du gyur ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-12: de nas ji ltar gyur pa thams cad khyim thab la bsnyad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-13: de thos nas des kyang bcom ldan 'das la dad pa rnyed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-14: de nas re zhig na bu mo des mthar gyis khyim thab la gsol te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-15: bcom ldan 'das kyi bstan pa la rab tu byung nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-18: 'bad pas phol mig lnga pa'i 'khor ba'i 'khor lo 'di nyid g-yo zhing mi brtan par rig nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-19: 'du byed kyi rnam pa thams cad rnyil ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:335b-22: rnam par 'jig pa'i chos can yin par rtsad chod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-1: spangs nas dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-2: dgra bcom pa khams gsum pa'i 'dod chags dang bral bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-4: bong bar mnyam pa; nam mkha' dang lag mthil du 'dra ba'i sems dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-5: tsandan spangs pa lta bur bsil bar gyur pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-6: rig pas sgo nga'i spubs bcom pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-9: so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-14: nye dbang dang bcas pa'i lha rnams kyis mchod cing rjed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-15: gus par smra ba'i gnas su gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-16: de nas dge slong dag the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-17: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-19: ra sthas las gang dag bgyis na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-20: des phyug po'i rigs su skyes lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-21: las gang dag bgyis na des mi sdug par gyur la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-22: rab tu byung nas dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du bgyis lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-23: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-25: ra stha nyid kyis sngon tshe rabs gzhan dag tu tshogs rnyed cing rkyen grub pa dang ldan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-26: dba' rgal bzhin du 'byung la gdon mi za bar 'ong ba'i las de dag byas shing bsags bas na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336a-27: ra stha nyid kyi las byas shing bsags pa de dag gzhan su zhig gis nyams su myong bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-0: @336b las byas shing bsags pa rnams ni phyi rol gyi sa'i khams la rnam par smin bar mi 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-3: rlung gi khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-4: las dge ba dang mi dge ba byas shing bsags pa rnams ni zin pa'i phung po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-6: skye mched rnams 'ba' zhig la rnam par smin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-7: lus can dag gi las rnams ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-8: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-9: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-12: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-13: grong khyer w'a ra n'a si na tshong dpon gyi chung ma gtum zhing brlang la gzu lum can zhig 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-14: sangs rgyas rnams 'jig rten du mi 'byung ba'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-15: rang sangs rgyas sdug cing phongs pa rnams la snying brtse ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-16: bas mtha'i gnas mal gyis 'tsho ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-17: 'jig rten na yon gnas gcig pu rnams 'jig rten du 'byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-18: de nas re zhig na rang sangs rgyas mi sdug pa zhig de'i khyim du song ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-19: des mi sdug pa 'di lta bu nga'i khyim du ci 'dod ces spyos mang du brgyad nas khyim nas bskrad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-20: de nas rang sangs rgyas des de la phan gdags pa'i phyir /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-21: ngang pa'i rgyal po 'dab ma brkyang ba bzhin du nam mkha' la mngon par 'phags nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:336b-22: cho 'phrul rnam pa sna tshogs bstan to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-0: de nas tshong dpon gyi chung ma 'gyod pa skyes nas de la gzod pa gsol @337a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-1: te; bshos kyang phul nas smon lam btab pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-2: bdag gis rang sangs rgyas la spyos brgyad pa de'i las kyi rnam par smin pa myong bar ma gyur cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-3: 'di lta bu'i chos dag kyang thob par gyur cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-4: 'di las kyang khyad par du 'phags pa'i ston pa mnyes par gyur cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-5: mi mnyes par byed par ma gyur cig ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-8: de'i tshe de'i dus na tshong dpon gyi chung mar gyur pa gang yin pa de ni ra stha 'di yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-9: der rang sangs rgyas la bshos phul ba de'i las kyi rnam par smin pas ni rgyal po phyug po'i rigs su skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-10: mi sdug pa'i tshig smras te //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-11: khyim nas bskrad pa des ni mi sdug par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-13: bcom ldan 'das 'od srung gi ring la rab tu byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-14: des der bslabs shing kha don du byas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-15: phung po la mkhas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-17: skye mched la mkhas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-18: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba la mkhas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-20: gnas ma yin pa la mkhas par byas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-21: tshangs par spyod pa'i gnas bsrungs pa des ni da ltar dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas so; ;dge slong dag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337a-22: de ltar na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams ni rnam par smin pa'ang gcig tu nges par gnag par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-0: las gcig tu nges par dkar ba rnams @337b ni rnam par smin pa rang gcig tu nges par dkar bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-1: las 'dres ma rnams ni rnam par smin pa yang 'dres mar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-3: de bas na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-5: las gcig tu nges par dkar pa rnams 'ba' zhig la gtad par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-7: khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-8: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-9: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-10: gang po la sogs pa'i rtog pa brjod pa brgya pa las /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-11: sdom gyi tshigs su bcad pa brgyad pa rdzogs so ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-13: rgya mtsho dang ni snam dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-14: lag na gser thogs sde snod gsum //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-15: grags bshes rdzus te skyes pa dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-16: mdzes ldan dang ni ka pi na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-17: bzang ldan dang ni yul 'khor bsrung /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-18: sde tshan dag tu bstan pa yin //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-19: rgya mtsho zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-20: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-21: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-23: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:337b-32: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-8: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-15: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-16: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-17: de'i tshe mnyan du yod pa na ded dpon zhig gnas pa des rigs mnyam pa las chung ma blangs nas de de dang lhan cig tu rtse zhing dga' la dga' mgur spyod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-18: de rtse zhing dga' la dga' mgur spyod pa las re zhig na de'i sems skyes pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-19: bdag ji srid du lang tshol bab pa de srid du ni nor spel bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-20: phyis rgas pa'i tshe ni bde bar longs spyod par bya'o snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-21: de nas ded dpon de g-yog 'khor tshong pa lnga brgya dang rgya mtsho'i gru nyos nas chung ma dang bcas te rgya mtsho chen po'i nang du zhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-22: de nas re zhig na de'i chung ma la bu chags nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-23: rgya mtsho de nyid kyi nang du bu byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338a-24: khye'u gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa zhig btsas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-0: de nas de btsas pa'i btsas ston byas @338b nas; ming rgya mtsho zhes btags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-1: de nas re zhig na ded dpon de gru don grub nas nye zho med par rgya mtsho chen po nas phyir 'khor te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-2: de nas gang gi tshe khye'u rgya mtsho cher skyes pa de'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-3: phas ded dpon du bskos nas g-yog 'khor tshong pa lnga brgya dang rgya mtsho chen por btang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-4: de mthar gyis song song ba las /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-10: tshong 'dus rnams mthong nas rgya mtsho'i 'gram du phyin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-11: k'a ra sha pa na lnga brgyas gru'i gla byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-12: zho shas 'tsho ba rnam pa lnga ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-13: gru shol ba dang; chu 'phyag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-16: ru skya 'dzin pa rnams kyang khrid de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-17: de lan gsum du dril bsgrags nas rgya mtsho chen por zhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-18: de nas de dag rgya mtsho chen por song ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-19: srin po nag po'i rlung gis gru de phu mdar bskor to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-20: ded dpon rgya mtsho ni mu stegs can la dga' ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-21: de dus ma yin par 'chi bas 'jigs skrag nas; ston pa drug la gsol ba 'debs pa la zhugs kyang gru de rlung gis ye bskor to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-22: de nas re zhig na tshong pa gzhan dag kyang lha stong snyed la gsol ba 'debs pa la zhugs te smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-23: gu lang chu lha ku be ra dang rlung lha me lha dbang chen dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:338b-24: drang srong sna tshogs lha dang sa la gnas pa'i klu mang de dag la //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-0: bdag cag dad pa lags kyi bdag cag 'di @339a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-2: myur du sdug bsngal 'di dag bsal te 'gron po rnams ni bskyab par gsol //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-3: de nas de dag gis de ltar smre sngags bton kyang skyabs byed pa su'ang med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-4: de nas re zhig na dge bsnyen zhig gru de'i nang na 'dug pa des smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-7: lha gzhan dag gis kyang khyed la ci byar yang med kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-8: mngon sum du yod pa'i lha sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la snying nas skyabs su song zhig dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-9: de khyed kyi skyabs su 'gyur ro zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-10: de nas ded dpon rgya mtsho la sogs pa tshong pa lnga brgya po rnams kyis skad bsnyams te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-11: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la skyabs su song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-12: de'i skabs su sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis ni mi mkhyen pa'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-15: thugs su mi chud pa ci yang med la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-16: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-17: 'jig rten la phan 'dogs pa la zhugs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-18: srung ba gcig pa dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-23: lhag mthong la gnas pa; rig pa gsum snang bar mdzad pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-24: bslab pa gsum la legs par bslabs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-25: 'dul ba'i gzhi gsum la mkhas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339a-26: chu bo bzhi las brgal ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-0: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa @339b bzhi'i zhabs kyi mthil shin tu brtan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-1: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi la yun ring po nas 'dris par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-3: khyu mchog gi yang dag pa'i seng ge'i sgra chen po sgrogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-4: yan lag lnga rnam par spangs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-5: 'gro ba lnga las yang dag par 'das pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-6: yan lag drug dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-7: pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-8: rtag tu gnas par bya ba drug la gnas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-9: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun gyi me tog gis phyug pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-10: lam yan lag brgyad pa ston pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-11: mthar gyis snyoms par 'jug pa dgu la mkhas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-12: stobs bcu'i stobs dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-13: phyogs bcur grags pas kun tu rgyas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-14: brgya phrag bcu la dbang byed pa bas ches khyad par du 'phags pa rnams ni chos nyid kyis nyin dus gsum /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-15: mtshan dus gsum du sangs rgyas kyi spyan gyis 'jig rten la gzigs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-19: su ni nyam nga bar gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-20: su ni gnod pa dang ldan /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-21: su ni phongs pa dang; nyam nga ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-23: su ni ngan song du gzhol /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-25: su ni ngan song du bab /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-26: su ni ngas ngan song nas phyung ste mtho ris dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:339b-29: su ni 'dod pa'i 'dam du bying pa las la gnas drang bar bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-0: su ni 'phags pa'i nor bdun med pa las 'phags pa'i nor bdun gyi dbang phyug @340a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-1: la dbang byed du gzhug par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-2: su ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams ma bskyed pa las bskyed par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-3: su ni dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams bskyed zin pa las yongs su smin par bya /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-4: su ni yongs su smin zin pa las rnam par grol bar bya snyam du ye shes gzigs pa 'jug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-6: rgya mtsho chu srin rnams kyi gnas //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-7: dus rlabs yol bar 'gyur yang srid //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-8: gdul bar bya ba'i sras rnams la //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-9: sangs rgyas dus las yol ba med //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:340a-10: de nas re zhig na bcom ldan 'das rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal na bzhugs pas nyi ma stong pas lhag pa'i 'od gser gyi kha dog lta bu'i 'od zer bkye nas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:378b-3: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:378b-6: bde bar gshegs pa; 'jig rten mkhyen pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:378b-7: skyes bu gdul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:378b-11: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnam par gzigs zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:378b-13: de nas re zhig na ded dpon zhig gis rgya mtsho chen po'i nang nas rin po che mang pa khyer te 'ongs nas des yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa zla ba gsum gyi bar du bshos la spyan drangs so; ;gtsug lag khang yang brtsigs nas phyogs bzhi'i dge 'dun la phul lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:378b-16: de'i tshe de'i dus na ded dpon du gyur pa gang yin pa de ni ka pi na 'di yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:378b-18: ka pi nas ni las gzhan dag kyang byas shing bsags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:378b-20: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na grong khyer w'a ra n'a si na rgyal po tshangs pas byin zhes bya ba rgyal po byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379a-2: mi mang pos gang ba dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379a-15: chos kyi rgyal po chos bzhin du rgyal po byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379a-16: de phyi zhig na blon po khri brgyad stong gis zhabs 'bring byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379a-17: skyed mos tshal gyi shing rnams me tog rgyas la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379a-24: shang shang te'u rnams skad 'byin pa'i nags khrod du song ba las des skyed mos tshal der rang sangs rgyas nad pa zhig mthong nas des de la zla ba gsum gyi bar du phan pa'i zas kyis bsnyen bkur byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379a-25: yongs su mya ngan 'das pa'i 'og tu'ang de'i sku gdung gi mchod rten brtsigs nas blon po'i tshogs dang bcas pas til mar gyis bskus te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379a-26: des na 'khor dang bcas pa tshan po che'i stobs dang ldan par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379a-28: sangs rgyas 'od srung gi ring la rab tu byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379a-29: des der dbang po yongs su smin par byas pa des na /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-2: de ltar na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams ni rnam par smin pa'ang gcig tu nges par gnag par 'gyur ro //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-6: de bas na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-8: las gcig tu nges par dkar ba rnams 'ba' zhig la gtad par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-10: khyod kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-12: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-13: bzang ldan zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-14: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-15: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-17: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:379b-26: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-5: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-12: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-13: de nas gang gi tshe bcom ldan 'das mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas lo bcu gnyis lon te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-16: bdud rtsi zas la sogs pa sh'akya stong phrag du mas bden pa mthong ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-17: rgyal po zas gtsang ni ma gtogs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-18: de nas rgyal po zas gtsang gis sras kyi legs pa de dag mthong nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-19: mchog tu ya mtshan du gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-21: gal te bdag gi bu rab tu ma byung du zin na ni 'di 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po mtha' bzhir rgyal ba chos dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-22: chos kyi rgyal por 'gyur ba zhig na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380a-23: da ni 'di thor tshugs can rab tu byung ba'i g-yog byas pa ni rab tu mi mdzes kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-0: bdag @380b gis sh'akya rnams las khyim re mi re rab tu 'byung du gzhug gor ma chag snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-1: de nas rgyal po zas gtsang gis sh'akya thams cad bsdu ba'i phyir grong khyer du dril bsgrags so; ;de nas sh'akya thams cad 'dus pa'i nang du rgyal po zas gtsang gis smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-2: kye; sh'akya khyed rnams nyon cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-3: gal te gzhon nu don thams cad grub pa rab tu ma byung du zin na'ang khyed kho nas 'di la bsnyen bkur bya dgos na da 'dir rab tu byung gi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-4: sh'akya khyim res mi res bsnyen bkur bya ba'i phyir rab tu phyung zhig ces byas so; ;de nas bzang ldan dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-7: lha sbyin la sogs pa sh'akya'i bu lnga brgya rab tu 'byung bar chas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-8: de nas de dag gi 'dreg mkhan bsnyen bkur byed pa nye bar 'khor des de dag rab tu 'byung ba mthong nas dus so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-9: de nas sh'akya rnams kyis nye bar 'khor khyod ci'i phyir du zhes dris so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-10: de nas des snying rje rje skad zer zhing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-13: khyed rab tu byung na da bdag la zas dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-14: gos skyong ba su zhig mchis /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-15: de nas sh'akya rnams kyis smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-17: 'o na ras thing zhig byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:380b-18: de nas des ras bting nas sh'akya rnams kyis lus la thogs pa'i do shal dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-3: sor rdub rnams phung po chen por spungs te byin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-4: de nas 'dreg mkhan nye bar 'khor gyis rab tu 'byung ba de dag kyang mthong la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-5: rgyan rnam pa sna tshogs la'ang bltas nas tshul bzhin du yid la byed pa skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-6: sh'akya 'di dag ni cho rigs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-9: 'byor pa dang ldan pa yin na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-11: rgyan 'di dag mchil ma bzhin du bor nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-12: rab tu byung na bdag ci'ang mi bdog pa zhig gis da rgyan 'di dag khyim du bskur du ci yod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-13: 'di dag btang la bdag kyang 'di dag gi rjes su rab tu 'byung gor ma chag snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-14: de nas 'dreg mkhan nye bar 'khor bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-15: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag btsal te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-16: bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-18: gal te bdag cag lta bu'ang legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu 'byung ba mchis la rab tu 'byung ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-19: bsnyen par rdzogs shing dge slong gi dngos po thob tu rung na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381a-20: bdag kyang bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du tshangs par spyod pa spyad par 'tshal lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-0: @381b ces byas pas rab tu phyung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-1: de nas bzang ldan la sogs pa sh'akya lnga brgya dge slong gi cha lugs can rnams sangs rgyas la sogs pa dge slong gi dge 'dun la phyag 'tshal bar byas pa las /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-2: de dag gis nye bar 'khor gyi rkang pa ngo shes nas cho rigs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-4: 'byor pa dang ldan pa'i phyir nye bar 'khor la phyag 'tshal du ma btub nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-5: der bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa bzang ldan la bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-7: gang gi phyir nga'i bstan pa 'di la ni cho rigs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-11: rigs bzhi rnam par dag pa dang sbyar ba med kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-13: de nas bzang ldan la sogs pa sh'akya lnga ba rgyas chos nyid btsan par byas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-14: sdong po rtsa ba nas bcad pa bzhin du rkang pa la phyag byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-15: de dag gis rkang pa la phyag byas pa'i mod la sa chen po 'di rnam pa drug tu g-yos so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-16: de nas der tshe dang ldan pa bzang ldan gyis brtson pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-18: 'bad pas phol mig lnga pa'i 'khor ba'i 'khor lo 'di nyid g-yo zhing mi brtan par rig nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-19: 'du byed kyi rnam pa thams cad snyil ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:381b-22: rnam par 'jig pa'i chos can yin par rtsad chod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-2: dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-3: dgra bcom pa khams gsum pa'i 'dod chags dang bral bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-7: lag mthil du 'dra ba'i sems dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-8: tsandan spangs pa lta bur bsil bar gyur pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-9: rig pas sgo nga'i sbubs bcom pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-12: so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-15: bkur sti la mi lta ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-17: nye dbang dang bcas pa'i lha rnams kyis mchod cing rjed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-18: gus par smra ba'i gnas su gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-19: de'ang bdag nyid che ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-20: sdug cing phongs pa rnams la snying brtse ba zhig ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-21: phyi zhig na snga dro sham thabs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-22: chos gos bgos te lhung bzed thogs nas mnyan du yod par spyod yul la chas so; ;de nas re zhig na rigs ngan zhig gi khyim du bsod snyoms la song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-23: de'i tshe ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal glang po che'i gtso bo padma dkar po gcig pu zhes bya ba la zhon te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382a-24: kha lo pa rgyu ba'i bu ring po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-0: bcom ldan 'das la blta ba'i phyir chas pa las ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis bzang @382b ldan dbang po zhi ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-2: sems mchog tu dul zhing nye bar zhi ba dang ldan la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-3: phyag dar khrod kyi gos gyon zhing kha zas ngan pa khyer te rigs ngan gyi khyim de nas phyir byung ba mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-4: mthong nas kyang kha lo rgyu ba'i bu ring po la dris pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-5: 'di dge slong bzang ldan ma yin nam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-10: de nas ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal khams nas brgyal te sa la lhung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-11: de nas chus gtor ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-12: phyir sangs te sems rtas nas kha lo pa rgyu ba'i bu ring pos bslang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-13: de nas rgyal po gsal rgyal bcom ldan 'das kyi thad du song ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-14: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag btsal nas bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-16: bdag gis ni rmad du byung ba zhig mthong ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-17: sh'akya'i rgyal po bzang ldan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-18: phyag dar khrod kyi gos gyon zhing kha zas ngan pa thogs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-20: mi dad par bgyi ba'i spyod lam shin tu zhi bas bsod snyoms blangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-21: rigs ngan gyi khyim nas slar byung ba de la bdag 'di snyam bgyid do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-22: bcom ldan 'das kyi bstan pa ni shin tu dul bar bgyid pa lags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:382b-23: de la bsten na 'di lta bur skyid de mchis la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-1: dag kyang 'di ltar tshul dul bar gyur pa ni ngo mtshar che'o snyam bgyid do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-4: bzang ldan 'di la ni ngo mtshar che ba gzhan yang yod kyi nyon cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-6: bzang ldan 'di ni dgon pa na gnas sam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-8: khang stong na gnas kyang rung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-11: bdag rab tu ma byung ba tsam na rgyal po'i pho brang gi nang na 'dug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-14: yul gyi mi rnams kyis shin tu legs par bsrungs la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-18: gcan rnams kyis bskyabs kyang snying gzhan la dogs shing mi dga' la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-19: kun la'ang khu 'phrig za bzhin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-21: da ni bdag lus dang srog la'ang mi lta bas gnas gang dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-22: gang du'ang bde bar 'dug tu yod ngo zhes dga' ba'i tshig lan gsum du rjod par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-23: de nas dge slong dag the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-24: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-26: bzang ldan gyis sngon tshe rabs gzhan dag tu las gang dag bgyis shing bsags na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383a-27: des gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-0: rgyal @383b po'i rigs phyug por skyes la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-1: rab tu byung nas kyang dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du bgyis lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-4: bzang ldan nyid kyis sngon tshe rabs gzhan dag tu tshogs rnyed cing rkyen grub pa dang ldan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-5: dba' rgal bzhin du 'byung la gdon mi za bar 'ong ba'i las de dag byas shing bsags pas na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-6: bzang ldan nyid kyis las byas shing bsags pa de dag gzhan su zhig gis nyams su myong bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-8: las byas shing bsags pa rnams ni phyi rol gyi sa'i khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-11: rlung gi khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-13: mi dge ba byas shing bsags pa ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-16: skye mched rnams 'ba' zhig la rnam par smin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-17: lus can dag gi las rnams ni; ;bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-18: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-21: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na grong khyer w'a ra n'a si na sprang po zhig gnas pa lus bkres shing nyam chung bas non nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:383b-22: phan tshun du 'khor 'khor ba las bu mo 'khur ba khyer ba zhig mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-1: 'khur ba 'dod pa'i phyir bu mo de bsnyegs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-2: nan gyis 'khur ba cig phrogs nas phan tshun du bros so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-3: bu mo de'ang de'i phyi bzhin 'brang bzhin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-4: de nas sprang po des tsham tshom med par chu klung zlog byed la 'bogs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-5: sangs rgyas rnams mi 'byung ba'i tshe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-6: rangs sangs rgyas sdug cing phongs pa rnams la snying brtse ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-7: bas mtha'i gnas mal gyis 'tsho ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-8: 'jig rten gyi yon gnas gcig pu rnams 'jig rten du 'byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-9: re zhig na rang sangs rgyas shig sprang po de'i mdun du 'ongs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-10: de nas sprang po des rang sangs rgyas spyod lam zhi ba de mthong nas dga' ba chen po skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-11: de dga' ba chen pos rang gi sdug bsngal dang bsngos te rang sangs rgyas la 'khur ba de phul lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:384a-12: de nas rang sangs rgyas des de'i dga' brgya chen po bskyed pa'i phyir /
