K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-0: nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs nas dgra bcom @410b pa nyid mngon sum du byas nas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-1: dgra bcom pa khams gsum pa'i 'dod chags dang bral bar gyur nas gser dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-4: lag mthil du 'dra ba'i sems dang ldan pa; tsandan spangs pa lta bur bsil bar gyur pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-5: rig pas sgo nga'i sbubs bcom pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-8: so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-11: bkur sti la mi lta ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-13: nye dbang dang bcas pa'i lha rnams kyis mchod cing rjed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-14: gus par smra ba'i gnas su gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-15: de nas phyis re zhig na bcom ldan 'das kyi dri gtsang khang phyag pa la zhugs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-16: des de phyags nas sham thabs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-18: lhung bzed thogs nas mnyan du yod par bsod snyoms la song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-19: de nas des bsod snyoms bzang po mang po dag rnyed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-20: des de'i dbang po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-21: 'byung ba chen po rnams tshim par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-22: de nas de dbang po tshim par gyur nas bsam gtan dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-24: snyoms par 'jug pa rnams kyis mtshan rangs pa 'das par byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-25: de nas de'i blo skyes pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-27: thabs 'di ni bzang po zhig gi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-28: bdag gis dge slong gi dge 'dun la gsol ba gdab bo snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-29: de nas des dge slong gi dge 'dun thams cad la gsol ba btab pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:410b-31: bdag ni bsod nams chung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-0: gang gi tshe dri gtsang khang du phyag dar bgyis nas bsod @411a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-1: snyoms la mchis pa de'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-3: de bas na bdag la dge 'dun gyi thugs brtse bar mdzod la gzhan sus kyang dri gtsang khang du phyag dar mi mdzad par gsol zhes byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-4: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi dri gtsang khang du sus kyang phyag dar mi bya'o zhes dge 'dun gyi khrims bcas nas des bag yangs su dri gtsang khang phyags pa'i 'og tu mnyan du yod par bsod snyoms la 'gro bar byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-5: de'i tshe na tshe dang ldan pa sh'a ri'i bu yang 'khor lnga brgya dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-6: rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal du dbyar gnas par dam bcas nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-7: mnyan du yod par lhags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-8: ston pa la gus pa skyes nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-9: dri gtsang khang du phyag dar byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-10: de nas tshe dang ldan pa 'de gus gsos kyis tshor nas des smras pa; gnas brtan khyod kyis dri gtsang khang du phyag dar byas pa ni bdag gi ltor bsnun par bas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-14: gnas brtan gang gi tshe bdag gi dri gtsang khang du phyag dar ma byas pa de'i tshe bdag gis bsod snyoms mi rnyed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-15: de nas gnas brtan sh'a ri'i bus smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-16: gal te de ltar na bdag ga zhig tu g-yar drangs kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-17: khyod snying ma chung zhig dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411a-18: bdag gis der khyod la kha zas sbyin par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-0: de nas gnas brtan sh'a ri'i bu 'khor lnga brgya dang bcas pa'i spyan 'dren 'ongs nas @411b 'de gus gsos kyang de dang lhan cig tu chas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-1: de nas gang gi tshe khyim bdag de'i sgo dang nye ba zhig tu phyin pa de'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-2: 'de gus gsos kyi las kyi rnam par smin pas khyim der 'thab mo chen po byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-3: de nas tshe dang ldan pa 'de gus gsos 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-4: bdag bsod nams chung ba'i phyir 'thab mo byung ngo snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-5: de nas phyir log ste gtsug lag khang du song nas smyung bar 'dug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-6: de nas phyi de nyin par tshe dang ldan pa sh'a ri'i bus smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-9: bdag bsod nams chung ba'i phyir 'thab mo ji ltar byung ba gnas brtan gyis mi mkhyen tam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-10: de nas gnas brtan sh'a ri'i bus de'i nyin par mdun du bcug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-11: khyim de'i nang du song nas dge 'dun gyi khrod du 'dug na yang g-yas g-yon ni kha zas brims la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-12: de la ni 'drim pa'i mis kyang brjed nas de dge 'dun gyi khrod de kho nar lan gnyis su smyung bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-13: de nas re zhig na gtam de gnas brtan kun dga' bos thos so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-14: thos nas kyang 'de gus gsos la smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-16: khyod rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal 'di nyid du 'dug cig dang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-17: bdag gis khyod kyi zas khyer te 'ong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:411b-19: gnas brtan kun dga' bo ni bcom ldan 'das las chos kyi phung po brgyad khri lobs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-0: dge slong gzhan dag las nyi khri lobs pa de lta bu'i dran pa dang ldan pa @412a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-2: 'de gus gsos kyi las kyi sgrib pas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-3: gnas brtan kun dga' bos kyang brjed par gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-4: der yang de lan gsum smyung bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-5: de nas zhag bzhi lon pa'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-6: gnas brtan kun dga' bos bsgrims te bsod snyoms byin na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-7: de yang phyir 'gro ba'i tshe khyi rnams kyis 'phrogs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-8: der yang de lan bzhi smyung bar gyur to; ;de nas zhag lnga lon pa'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-9: gnas brtan mo'u dgal gyi bu chen pos thos nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-10: 'de gus gsos kyi phyir bsod snyoms blangs nas rdzu 'phrul gyis chas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-11: 'de gus gsos kyi las kyi rnam par smin pas bya'i rgyal po nam mkha' lding gis 'dab lcag gis bsnun nas rgya mtsho'i nang du bor te der yang lan lnga smyung bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-12: de nas zhag drug lon pa'i tshe gnas brtan sh'a ri'i bus thos nas de 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-14: bdag kho nas 'de gus gsos kyi bsod snyoms blangs gor ma chag snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-15: de nas gnas brtan sh'a ri'i bus de'i bsod snyoms blangs nas khyim de nyid du mi snang bar byas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-16: 'de gus gsos kyi gnas khang gi sgor 'ongs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-17: de na 'de gus gsos kyi las kyi rnam par smin pas sgo de yang brag gis 'khor bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412a-18: de nas gnas brtan sh'a ri'i bus rdzu 'phrul gyi sgo dbye'o snyam nas lhung bzed des la bzhag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-0: de yang 'de gus gsos kyi las kyi rnam par @412b smin pas thur du dpag tshad brgyad khri'i 'og na gser gyis gzhi yod pa'i steng du song nas de las kyang gnas brtan sh'a ri'i bus rdzu 'phrul gyis phyung nas zas de khar gzhug go snyam ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-1: zas de khar bcug na de'i las kyi rnam par smin pas kha de med par phyi la bor bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-2: de nas tshe dang ldan pa sh'a ri'i bu 'de gus gsos la skal ba med par shes nas skyo bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-3: der yang btsun pa de lan drug smyung bar gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-4: de nas zhag bdun lon pa'i nyin par tshe dang ldan pa 'de gus gsos kyis sems can rnams skyo ba bskyed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-5: las rnams chud mi za par bstan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-6: las kyi stobs gleng ba'i phyir lhung bzed thal bas bkang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-7: sangs rgyas la sogs pa dge slong gi dge 'dun gyi spyan sngar 'dug nas chu dang bskyos te 'thungs nas phung po'i lhag ma med pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings su mya ngan las 'das so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-8: de nas dge slong rnams kyis de mthong nas skyo bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-9: de'i sku gdung la sku gdung gi mchod pa byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-10: de nas dge slong dag the tshom skyes te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-11: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-13: 'de gus gsos kyis las gang dag bgyis na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-14: der dgra bcom pa nyid thob par gyur kyang zhag drug smyung bar gyur nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:412b-15: zhag bdun pa'i gdugs la phung po'i lhag ma med pa'i dbyings su yongs su mya ngan las 'das lags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-3: 'de gus gsos nyid kyi sngon tshe rabs gzhan dag tu tshogs rnyed cing rkyen grub pa dang ldan te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-4: dpa' rgal bzhin du 'byung la gdon mi za bar 'ong ba'i las de dag byas shing bsags na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-5: 'de gus gsos nyid kyis las byas shing bsags pa de dag gzhan su zhig gis nyams su myong bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-7: las byas shing bsags pa rnams ni phyi rol gyi sa'i khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-10: rlung gi khams la rnam par smin par mi 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-12: mi dge ba byas shing bsags pa rnams ni zin pa'i phung po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-14: skye mched rnams 'ba' zhig la rnam par smin par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-15: lus can dag gi las rnams ni //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-16: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-17: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-20: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na; grong khyer w'a ra na si na khyim bdag gcig gi chung ma dad pa dang ldan la dge zhing bsam pa bzang ba zhig 'dug pa de rgyun mi 'chad par dge slong dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-24: slong pa rnams la sbyin pa dag byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413a-25: phyis de'i khyim thab shi nas re zhig na de'i bu bdag gi khyim gyi bdag por gyur to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-0: de yang ser sna can 'jungs @413b pa; yo byad la kun tu 'dzin pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-1: khva la yang gtor ma mi ster ba zhig ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-6: slong ba rnams mthong na sems sdang bar byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-7: de'i ma ni sngon gyi lugs bzhin du dge sbyong dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-11: slong ba rnams la sbyin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-12: rab tu sbyin pa dag sbyin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-13: de nas de'i bu ser snas non pa des smras pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-15: bdag ma dad kyi sbyin pa ma byin cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-18: khyim 'di na khyim gyi lugs kyis de yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-19: de nas de logs shig tu zan phog ste bzhag na 'on kyang de zan gyi phyed ni sbyin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-21: de nas ser snas non cing khro bas bsgribs pa'i blo can des yang dang yang du bkag ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-22: thabs ji lta bus bkag kyang de dgags ma nus nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-25: bgyi ba zhig mchis kyi khyim gyi phug tu bzhud cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-26: de nas rang bzhin gyis drang ba de khyim gyi phug tu song ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-27: de nas des sgo bcad de nyi ma gcig zan gcad nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-31: de nas de tshig rtsub po smras te thal ba 'gom zhig ces smras so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:413b-32: de nas re zhig na nyam nga zhing mi bde la gnod pa dang phrad pa des snying rje rje skad du khus btab kyang zhag drug gi bar du smyung du bcug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-0: 'on kyang ser snas bsgribs pa de ma dang bral ba la 'gyod @414a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-5: de'i tshe de'i dus na khyim bdag gi bur gyur pa gang yin pa de ni 'di gus gsos 'di yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-6: des ma la gnod pa byas pa'i las de'i rnam par smin pas bskal ba gcig gi bar du sems can dmyal ba chen po mnar med par skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-7: rgyu de kho nas da ltar dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas kyang smyung bar gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-8: thal ba zos nas yongs su mya ngan las 'das so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-10: 'de gus gsos kyis las gzhan dag kyang byas shing bsags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-12: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na grong khyer w'a ra n'a si na bram ze lha la rten pa w'a ra na si na gnas pa'i bram ze dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-14: skye bo thams cad kun tu bkur sti bya ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-17: mchod pa byed cing bkur ba zhig yod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-18: chos nyid kyis na sangs rgyas rnams 'jig rten du mi 'byung ba'i tshe /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-19: rang sangs rgyas sdug cing phongs pa rnams la snying brtse ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-20: bas mtha'i gnas mal gyis 'tsho ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-21: 'jig rten gyi yon gnas gcig pu rnams 'jig rten du 'byung ste; re zhig na rang sangs rgyas gcig w'a ra n'a sir bsod snyoms la song ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-22: de der lag pa yang bkang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414a-24: phyir byung ba bram ze des mthong nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-0: de @414b ser sna skyes te lhung bzed blta yi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-1: tshur khyer shog ces byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-3: rang sangs rgyas rnams ni ma bsam par shes pa mi 'jug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-5: de nas des sa la pho nas rkang pas bsnun to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-6: de nas rang sangs rgyas de smyung bar 'dug kyang bram ze de 'gyod pa ma skyes so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-9: de'i tshe de'i dus na bram zer gyur pa gang yin pa de ni 'de gus gsos 'di yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-11: bcom ldan 'das 'od srung gi ring la rab tu byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-12: des der tshangs par spyod pa'i gnas bsrungs pa des na da ltar dgra bcom pa nyid mngon sum du byas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-14: de ltar na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams ni rnam par smin pa yang gcig tu nges par gnag par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-15: las gcig tu nges par dkar ba rnams ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-16: rnam par smin pa'ang gcig tu nges par dkar bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-17: las 'dres ma rnams ni rnam par smin pa yang 'dres mar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-19: de bas na las gcig tu nges par gnag pa rnams dang las 'dres ma rnams spangs la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-20: las gcig tu nges par dkar ba rnams 'ba' zhig la gtad par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-22: khyed kyis de ltar bslab par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-23: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:414b-24: dge slong de dag yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-0: @415a *// sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la rgyal po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-1: blon po chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-3: pho brang 'khor gyi mi rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-12: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis bkur stir byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-22: lto 'phye chen po rnams kyis mchod cing shes pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das bsod nams chen po dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-29: nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mnyan du yod pa na rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-30: de'i tshe mnyan du yod pa na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-31: khyim bdag phyug cing nor mang la longs spyod che ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-32: yongs su 'dzin pa yangs shing rgya che ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-33: rnam thos kyi bu'i nor dang ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-34: rnam thos kyi bu'i nor dang 'gran pa zhig gnas pa des rigs mnyam pa las chung ma blangs nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415a-35: de de dang lhan cig tu rtse zhing dga' la dga' mgur spyod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415b-0: de rtse zhing dga' @415b la dga' mgur spyod pa las chung ma la bu chags nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-075-001:415b-1: de zla ba brgyad dam dgu lon pa dang bu byung ste khye'u gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa /
